name: Ever System
statement: DApp游戏 加密忍者
statement_en: DApp Game Crypto Ninja
description: EverSystem研究和开发如何将先进技术高效应用到现实生活和商业场景中。
description_en: EverSystem does research and develop how advanced technology can be effectively utilized in real society and real business.

name: Staking.Global
statement: Make the network running
statement_en: Make the network running
description: Staking Global专注于相关公链的节点运营，旨在通过staking的方式为区块链的生态繁荣贡献力量。
description_en: Staking Global is focused on the node running on the public blockchains and contribute to the building of blockchain ecosystem by staking.

name: 火币矿池
statement: 以真诚的态度肩负起IOST生态建设的使命，维护网络安全可靠地运行，让更多的人了解IOST，参与到IOST社区建设。潜心做事，与更多节点一道助力IOST生态经济的起航。
statement_en: We will do our utmost efforts to carry out the mission of building up IOST ecosystem and maintaining the network security. We will help to market IOST and be fully involved in the IOST community development. We will concentrate on what we are doing and forge a synergy with other nodes to push the ship of the IOST sailing far and beyond.
description: 火币矿池是首家集数字货币开采与交易一体化的矿池平台。依托火币集团的强大资源，资金支持，拥有强大的研发实力与全球范围内的大量用户，容纳PoW、PoS和DPoS等多种共识机制 。
description_en: Huobi pool is the first-ever pool platform which combines cryptocurrency mining and exchanging activities. Backed by the powerful resources and financial support provided by Huobi Group, Huobi excels in R&D abilities and has a large user base around the world, and can accommodate various mechanisms such as PoW, PoS, and DPos.

name: 涅槃资本
statement: 希望IOST能够通过战略投资和落地产品来实现强大生态的构建，涅槃资本也将在此过程中为IOST提供信息和资源的全方位支持。涅槃资本将会利用在韩国、日本、俄罗斯、东南亚、非洲、北美等地的KOL影响力、本地传统资源及遍布全球的被投项目组成的强大的社区网络，与其他节点一道为IOST提供最坚实的后盾。在这样的市场环境下，能与你一起穿越牛熊的团队少之又少。如果你到今天还是IOST的持有者，那请坚持下去，时间会证明一切。
statement_en: We hope that IOST could build a powerful ecosystem through strategic investment and massive adoption of its products. Nirvana Capital, on the other hand, will give IOST all-around support either in resources or information sharing. Nirvana Capital will also leverage its KOL influence present in Korea, Japan, Russia, Southeast Asia, Africa, North America and other areas around the world, its local traditional resources and its investment projects around to push forward IOST’s future development.
description: 涅槃资本（Nirvana Capital）是一家专注于区块链、金融科技和其他早期科技项目一级市场投资的基金，现成员主要分布在湾区和北京，其创始人也是以太坊的早期支持者。为携各社区共同建造改变社会生产和劳动关系的生态系统，涅槃资本对其投资的项目提供全方位强有力支持，包括战略方向与生态运营的建议指导和市场资源对接。我们的区块链布局包括了layer 1和layer 2的基础设施，以及部分去中心化应用和生态内相关节点。
description_en: Nirvana Capital is a San Francisco/Beijing based blockchain fund that focuses on primary market investment and exploration in edging ideas of technology and economics. Its founding partners are also early supporters of Ethereum. To bring together ecosystems that revolutionize the social productions and labor relations with the communities underneath, Nirvana Capital provides end-to-end strong support to its portfolio projects, including advisory on strategies/operations and resources matching. Our blockchain development also covers layer 1 and layer 2 infrastructures, and some DApps and nodes within the ecosystem.

name: 节点资本
statement: 希望IOST可以在公链的竞争中可以突出重围，以高效、稳定、安全的底层技术为核心打造多元生态。节点资本也将整合现有资源进行支持，为IOST发展助力。
statement_en: We hope that IOST could excel in the league among public blockchains, and we believe IOST could build a diverse ecosystem with highly efficient, stable and safe technology at its core. Node Capital will also consolidate its resources to support IOST development.
description: 节点资本专注于区块链行业，是全球最早布局区块链产业生态的专业投资机构之一。旨在通过项目投资与合作，连接区块链生态上的关键节点，整合行业资源，构建生态圈，推动区块链行业健康稳健发展。截至目前，节点资本已经投资了近200家企业，覆盖了新闻资讯、交易所、区块链技术开发与应用、区块链数据挖掘与分析、第三方服务等生态系统中的众多项目，包括火币、金色财经、链上科技、库神钱包、降维安全、港盛科技、Bgogo、Bibox、标准共识、Hiwa等。
description_en: Node Capital is one of the world's earliest professional investment institutions focusing on blockchain industry. Node Capital aims to connect every node of blockchain industry by project investment and cooperation, build a robust industry ecosystem, and accelerate the development of blockchain industry.Node Capital has invested nearly 200 enterprises, and the number keeps growing rapidly. The portfolio of Node Capital encompassed projects from every corner of the blockchain ecosystem，such as exchanges, media, digital asset transactions, crypto asset wallet, technology development and application, blockchain data mining and analysis. The invested projects include Huobi, Jinse Finance, Chainup, Kushen Wallet, Dimensionality ReductionSecurity, Gangsheng Technology, Bgogo, Bibox, Standard Consensus, Hiwa, etc.

name: bishijie
statement: bishijie作为币圈最具影响力，用户最多的投资服务平台，始终致力于让用户投资更简单。我们将推动bishijie同城会，为IOST的DApp生态提供更强有力的社群力量。
statement_en: As the most influential and most user-friendly investment service platform, BiShiJie is always committed to making user investment easier. We will continue to expand BiShiJie City to the world and expand our community, and push forward IOST's DApp ecosystem building by mobilizing our community sources.
description:
bishijie是在中国最具影响力、用户最多的第一币圈投资服务平台。如今通过API给主流区块链APP、平台、传统媒体提供新闻，覆盖区块链用户达到300万左右。
其中bishijie同城会是bishijie独立打造的一个去中心化的分布式百万社群，旨在为进入区块链行业、参与数字经济的从业者及区块链爱好者提供一个线上线下交流、分享的机会。
bishijie同城会半年的时间，覆盖全国300个城市，建立1000+社群，拥有500000+区块链及币圈爱好者，赢得了用户良好的口碑和反响。
description_en:
BiShiJie is one of the most influential and popular cryptocurrency investment service platforms in China, and it delivers trade information 24/7 through API to mainstream blockchain-related APP, platforms and some traditional media platforms. Bishijie’s registered users have exceeded 3M. 
BiShiJie City is a decentralized million-member community independently built by BiShiJie, which aims to offer online and offline communication and sharing opportunities among blockchain& cryptocurrency practitioners and enthusiasts. 
Within a half year since its inception, BiShiJie City successfully entered 300 cities, built 1,000 plus communities with a user base of more than 500,000 members, which, during the process, has brought BiShiJie City popularity and praises.

name: IOST Pacific
statement: 我们是一支专注于治理、技术、培训的专业节点团队。社区治理很苦很累，但对于任何一个生态都不可或缺。我们有信心为IOST社区贡献这份不可取代的力量。相信区块链、相信IOST，参与其中，相信共识的力量，相信治理的力量。
statement_en: We are a team focusing on community governance, blockchain technology development and education. Community governance is a hard nut but is also an indispensable part in any ecosystem. We believe we will be irreplaceable in IOST ecosystem. We believe in blockchain’s future and we believe in IOST. Finally, we believe that consensus and governance will unleash its power sooner or later.
description: IOST Pacific是NodePacific Tech在IOST竞选的合伙人，NodePacific Tech是一家专业为公链做节点的公司。立足于亚太，在技术与治理领域有先发优势且有比较成功的经验。Node Pacific核心成员来自清华北大。团队成员来自博时基金、GE CAPITAL、华为研究院、腾讯、微软等知名互联网企业；平均有10多年的开发经验，目前专注于区块链方向。
description_en: IOST Pacific the tag of NodePacific Tech in the IOST partner election campaign. NodePacific Tech is dedicated to serving as the node for the public blockchain projects. Based in the Asia Pacific, we have accumulated much experience in blockchain technology and community governance over the years. Node Pacific's core members are from Tsinghua University and Peking University. Team members come from Bosera Funds, GE CAPITAL, Huawei Research Institute, Tencent, Microsoft and other well-known Internet enterprises; On average, they have more than 10 years of development experience and are currently focusing on the blockchain technology.

name: Endless@IOST
statement: Everybody wins here.
statement_en: Everybody wins here.
description: Endless@IOST是区块链游戏公司Endless Game在IOST网络上竞选的合伙人。Endless Game为玩家提供了不同种类的游戏选择，从简单的去中心化游戏，到更具吸引力的策略和RPG游戏等。玩家可以赚取真正意义上具有价值的代币，并通过玩我们的游戏获得终身利润分红。Endless Game正在与全球顶级游戏工作室合作，共同开发基于区块链的好玩的游戏。使用先进的跨链解决方案，玩家将来能够在不同的公链上玩游戏获得ET以及终身的利润分红。
description_en: Endless@IOST is the node for Endless Game who will campaign for being a partner on IOST network.Endless Game provides players with a vast choices of games, from simple dGames like dice to more engaging strategy and RPG games. With our next-gen gaming platform, players can earn tokens with real life value and get lifetime dividend by simply playing our games. Endless Game is working with top tier game studios globally to transform their games into dGames. Using advanced cross-chain solution, players will be able receive and use ET throughout all blockchains supported. Endless fun and joy, anywhere and anytime!

name: AlphaCoin Fund
statement: 我们愿与IOST积极合作，推动区块链技术在金融支付、物联网、传统制造业等各行业的应用落地，区块链的未来必然有IOST和Alphacoin Fund的一席之地。
statement_en: We are willing to carry out proactive cooperation with IOST and support IOST with utmost efforts on the adoption of its blockchain technology in financial payment, Internet of Things(IoT), and traditional manufacturing industry. We believe both IOST and Alphacoin Fund will be important players in the blockchain field.
description: AlphaCoin Fund注册成立于开曼，是一家专注于区块链技术和通证赋能的风险投资基金。团队成员来自全球顶尖数字货币交易所及金融机构（Binance、花旗银行）并拥有世界名校学术背景（康奈尔、哥伦比亚、南洋理工、清华）。自2017年以来，AlphaCoin Fund投资了全球范围内超50个优质的区块链项目，投资总额超过6000万美金。同时，AlphaCoin Fund已成为火币和CyberMiles和bgogo超级节点机构之一，也与真格基金、红杉资本、经纬中国、海纳亚洲、峰瑞资本、策源创投等一线投资机构深入建立了长期合作关系。此外，AlphaCoin股权战略投资布局了矿场矿池、软硬件钱包、流量平台、数字货币交易所及资管服务。AlphaCoin Labs将生态整合-区块链应用融合基金、区块链应用实验室、区块链应用与金融业对接和服务中心及行业高峰论坛，通过共享全球研究报告、行业培训、技术讲座、海内外高校产学研和举办区块链全球峰会等合作，打造海南省自由贸易试验区（港）区块链应用金融业融合品牌示范工程，建立具有全球影响力的区块链应用标志性研究机构。
description_en: AlphaCoin Fund was a venture capital fund founded in Cayman and is focused on blockchain startups and crypo-asset investments. Team members come from the world's top digital currency exchanges and financial institutions (Binance, Citibank), and have academic backgrounds from world-famous universities (Cornell, Columbia, Nanyang Technological Institute, Tsinghua University).We have invested over 50 high-quality blockchain projects since 2017, with the total amount of investment of over $60M. We are now the supernodes of Huobi Pro, CyberMiles, and bgogo. We also have built a long term relationship with Zhen Fund, Sequoia, Matrix Partners China, SIG Asia, FreeS Fund and Ceyuan Ventures. In addition, AlphaCoin's equity strategic investment covers mining pools, hardware and software wallets, traffic platforms, digital currency exchanges, and asset management services.AlphaCoin Labs will consolidate all resources, such as blockchain application fund, blockchain application labs and integrate blockchain technology and financial industry. We have been sharing our experience in global research on the industry, in training sessions, in tech workshop and are cooperating with universities at home and abroad and also have organized some influential global blockchain summits. Through the above-mentioned efforts, we are pushing forward to build a demonstration project with the integration of blockchain technology and financial industry and making it an iconic research institution of blockchain application in the world.

name: 币市
statement: 全球首家币币&币股交易所，USDT一键交易美股。
statement_en: World's First Token-to-Token&Token-to-Stock CFD Trading Platform. Trade stock/USDT by one click.
description: BISS.com是全球首家币币&币股交易所。
description_en: BISS.com is the first exchange that supports both cryptocurrency and stock.

name: BBX
statement: Make IOST Great Again
statement_en: Make IOST Great Again
description: BBX.COM是全球领先的加密货币指数合约交易平台，为全球超过100个国家和地区的用户提供安全、可信赖的加密货币衍生品交易服务。主要提供比特币、以太坊等一系列区块链资产的衍生品交易服务，核心团队来自腾讯、阿里、360、迅雷、雪球、老虎证券等公司，团队分布于马耳他，新加坡等全球多地办公。BBX.COM的愿景是能够为区块链资产投资者提供安全、便捷、专业、放心的衍生品交易服务。
description_en: BBX.COM is one of the world's leading digital asset exchanges. It mainly provides derivative trading services for a series of blockchain assets such as Bitcoin and Ethereum. The core teams are from Tencent, Alibaba, 360, Thunder, Snowball, Tiger Securities, etc., the team is located in Malta, Singapore and other places around the world. BBX.COM's vision is to provide blockchain asset investors with safe, convenient, professional and assured derivatives trading services.

name: DDEX
statement: DDEX 作为以太坊上最大的去中心化交易所，我们将会和IOST 共同努力， 为IOST 生态中的代币交易创建安全公开的交易平台。
statement_en: DDEX is the largest decentralized exchange on the Ethereum blockchain. We will work together with IOST and build a secure exchange platform in IOST ecosystem.
description: DDEX是以太坊网络上最大的去中心化交易所之一，转账数占全网去中心化交易的25%。同时也是首家基于Hydro协议技术的去中心化交易所，通过实时的链下撮合机制和安全的链上结算机制，为用户提供优质的交易体验。
description_en: DDEX is one of the largest decentralized exchanges on the Ethereum network, with 25% of the total decentralized transactions. It is also the first decentralized exchange based on Hydro protocol technology, providing users with a high-quality trading experience through a real-time chain-linking mechanism and a secure chain-based settlement mechanism.

name: 浮点资本
statement: 用区块链重新定义信任
statement_en: Redefine trust with blockchain.
description: 社区起源于币圈神秘狗头帮，曲曲折折经历了币圈几次牛熊的兄弟们，至今还紧紧在一起谈笑风生。浮点资本曾参与IOST的早期私募，看着币价起起伏伏，都不曾心动，因为我们坚信IOST一定会有更加伟大的未来。区块链就是未来，而IOST一定能在公链竞争之中占据一席之地。
description_en:
Community concept comes from a mysterious self-claimed organization called Gou Tou Bang. They are still united and talks about everything after all the cyclical ups and downs in the cryptocurrency market. As a partner of IOST, we have been involved in the IOST’s early private funding, and still remain unwaveringly determined even after cyclical bulls and bears in the crypto market as we believe in the future of IOST.
We firmly hold that blokchain is a transformative technology and IOST will excel in the showdown of public blockchains.

name: 3点钟
statement: 起源于区块链社群的3AM，从建立到发展都是基于用户共识而走到今天的，希望大家继续支持3AM，我们将为大家建设一个更加安全、可靠、开放、公正且充满乐趣的价值共享平台。
statement_en: 3AM comes into being from the blockcain communities, and we have been going through a long way and are still here thanks to user’s consensus. We hope you will continuously support us as we are striving to build a more secure, reliable, open, just and fair, and interesting value-sharing platform.
description: 3点钟是一款专注于区块链领域的生态开放平台，也是区块链领域第一流量入口，拥有完善的挖矿激励生态体系，支持数字钱包及小程序，同时支持第三方媒体和大V入驻等，聚合区块链行业优质合作伙伴，致力于打造区块链社群交流第一平台。
description_en: 3 AM is a open blockchain ecosystem platform and is also the first network traffic portal in the blockchain field. 3AM has put in place a comprehensive mining incentive ecosystem which supports digital wallets, small programs, third-party media and KOL. We have been working with high-quality partners in the blockchain industry. We are committed to building the first community platform for blockchain partners.

name: BlockVC
statement: 支持我们，你不仅会获得节点奖励的回馈，同样也会获得BlockVC整体战略布局和服务矩阵的优先支持。你不仅会获得简单的物质奖励，还将优先获得确保你在熊市中生存，在下一波牛市中一飞冲天的全方位资产管理服务和支持。支持BlockVC，赢得的不只是奖励，更是通往未来成功的机遇。你值得拥有。
statement_en: Vote for us! You will not only earn rewards but also will get primary support in the overall strategy and service matrix layout, which will help you to survive in the current bear market and stand out in the next bull run. Vote for us, and we will guide you to the way of success!
description: BlockVC 是全球领先的区块链风险投资机构，专注投资区块链领域的初创企业、加密资产和风险资本，在业内以专业度和国际化著称。BlockVC 系统地建立了“一二级市场联动”的投资哲学，并打造了专属的投资矩阵。投资方向覆盖了区块链生态系统中的基础公链、通用协议和金融服务等，为区块链项目提供从投资孵化到资产管理在内的全生命周期服务，所投资的项目均具备全球影响力。
description_en: BlockVC is a leading blockchain investment and digital asset management firm. We focus exclusively on projects, tokens and ventures related to blockchain technologies. BlockVC established a systematic investment philosophy of “primary-to-secondary market linkage” and created a proprietary investment matrix. The portfolio covers public blockchain, application protocols, and financial services in blockchain ecosystem. Besides, we provide a life-cycle services from project incubation to asset management. All the invested projects have a global and profound impact.

name: Link Node
statement: Born to be different
statement_en: Born to be different
description: Link Node是LinkVC作为IOST合伙人的子品牌。LinkVC成立于2016年，是一家具有全球视野的新锐风险投资基金，由林嘉鹏先生创立，总部位于新加坡，办公地点分布在北京、香港和旧金山等地。基金主要投资方向包括区块链技术、加密货币和金融科技。LinkVC致力于为区块链行业中最出色的的公司和开发者提供全球化的商业资源和专业的金融服务。在过去两年间，连接资本在全球范围投资了多个顶尖项目，包括Aicoin，BBX， BBEX，aelf，DigiFinex，IOST等等。
description_en: Link Node is operated as a IOST partner by LinkVC. LinkVC is a new cutting-edge venture capital with global view, founded in 2016 by MR.Jiapeng Lin. From our headquarter in Singapore all the way to offices in Beijing, HongKong and the San Francisco, we are dedicated to investing in blockchain technology, cryptocurrency and Fin-Tech.LinkVC committed to serving outstanding companies and developers in the field of blockchain with global commercial resources and professional financial services. In the past two years, linkVC invested dozens superior projects worldwide including Aicoin, BBX, BBEX, aelf, DigiFinex, IOST, etc.

name: IOST Bean
statement: 有优质落地应用的公链才是好公链，让 Spark Blockchain 的开发者社区帮助 IOST 更好成长！
statement_en: High-quality blockchains should have real use cases. The developer community of Spark Blockchain will support IOST’s development.
description: IOST Bean由知名孵化器Spark Blockchain 运营，其总部位于波士顿。Spark Blockchain 致力于孵化区块链底层解决方案以及区块链应用型初创公司，总部位于美国东北部的世界教育、人才之都波士顿。过往在美国举办过多次高质量大规模区块链峰会，共吸引过万高质量人群参与和关注。 Spark Blockchain 旗下有 GXChain 公信节点 GXBean（前11，理事会成员）、EOS 超级节点 EOS Bean、Tron 超级代表 TronBoston。Spark Blockchain 团队成员社区治理经验丰富，有 BitShares Core Team 成员，也活跃于GXChain 核心治理社区。
description_en: The IOST Bean is operated by the well-known incubator Spark Blockchain and is headquartered in Boston. Spark Blockchain is also based in Boston, the world's education and talent capital in the northeastern United States and is dedicated to incubating blockchain underlying solutions and blockchain application startups. Over the past years, we have held multiple high-quality large-scale blockchain summits in the United States, attracting over 10,000 top talents. Spark Blockchain has GXChain public node GXBean (top 11, board member), EOS super node EOS Bean, and Tron’s super representative TronBoston. Besides, the Spark Blockchain team members have extensive community governance experience and are members of the BitShares Core Team and they also are active in the GXChain core governance community.

name: IOST Fans
statement: 致力于IOST生态报道，发现IOST更多价值，我们每个人都是IOST Fans。
statement_en: We are dedicated to the real-time update of IOST’s ecosystem building and searching for more value of IOST. We are all IOST Fans.
description: IOST FANS是一个垂直于IOST 区块链的生态门户。IOST Fans为IOST生态提供丰富的服务，新闻快讯，IOST活动预告，IOST入门与开发，IOST项目团队与DAPP介绍，IOST节点选举与采访，IOST生态导航等。所有关于IOST的信息都可以在IOST Fans上找到。
description_en: IOST is an independant media plaftorm focusing on IOST ecosystem development. IOST Fans provides a wealth of services for IOST ecosystem, including newsletter, IOST event preview, IOST know-how and development, IOST project team and DApp introduction, IOST Partner election and interview and IOST eco-navigation. All information about IOST can be found on IOST Fans.

name: 超节点SSSminex
statement: SSSminex将拥护IOST的理念，维护IOST的权益，建设稳定安全共享收益的合伙人生态，加入我们，一同迎接区块链春天的到来！
statement_en: SSSminex believes in IOST’s core idea, safeguards the rights of IOST, and strives to build a partner ecosystem that is stable and secure. Join us to welcome the arrival of spring of blockchain technology!
description: SSSminex是SSSnodes与Minex.HK联合申请的IOST合伙人，将发挥深圳、香港两地的区块链资源和社区优势，建设优质和稳定的IOST合伙人。
description_en: SSSminex is the IOST Partner jointly applied by SSSnodes and Minex.HK, and we will make full use of our resources and community connections in Shen Zhen and HongKong to push forward IOST ecosystem development. We are determined to be IOST ’s high-quality and stable Partner.

name: Hydrogenesis
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: 永远的拜占庭！
statement_en: Byzantine forever!
description: 支持Jimmy！
description_en: We will support Jimmy as always!

name: DappReview
statement: 从DApp生态的开发者资源和DApp的推广发行等层面，DappReview将助力IOST一起推动DApp行业的大爆发。
statement_en: Together with IOST, DappReview will make every effort to helping Dapps developers and building Dapp ecosystem.
description: DappReview是全球最大的DApp生态平台，提供最精确的 DApp 数据，用户洞察和市场数据分析。目前已经支持超过6条公链的Dapp数据抓取分析和展示，收录了总计超过2000个DApp。同时作为DApp垂直领域的自媒体，DappReview已经输出了几十篇具有影响力的深度DApp评测和行业报道，并从DApp开发的技术讨论、运营推广以及投融资业务给予开发者全方位的帮助。
description_en: DappReview is the largest DApp platform in the world, delivering accurate DApp data, user insights and market analytics. Now support 6 public chains, tracking more than 2000 Dapps data. As one of the leading media dedicated to blockchain technology and DApps, DappReview provides professional reviews on new DApps and industry insights. We also provide Financial Advisors services and PR/marketing solutions for developers and DApp companies.

name: IOST广州
statement: 让更多的人知道区块链；让更多的人了解区块链；让更多的人参与区块链，是IOST广州孜孜以求的目标。IOST广州将依托自身全力推广IOST，让更多的用户使用IOST网络的DApp应用，与更多的IOST合伙人一道助力IOST的发展。IOST广州期待着您的加入，IOST广州和您一起创造未来!
statement_en: Getting more people to know about the blockchain technology and join IOST network has been always the ideal we are pursuing. Since the inception of this voluntary association, we have been making constant efforts to promote IOST and get IOST DApps to reach out to more people. We also have been working together with IOST partners to push forward its development. Please support IOST Guang Zhou Community to build a better IOST.
description: IOST广州作为广州地区的一个社区，一直致力于区块链的推广、教育工作。社区运营2年来，积累了大量社员，在这里社员们一起学习、交流、探索，形成了一个开放的区块链爱好者之家。
description_en: IOST Guangzhou is dedicated to IOST promotion. Over the last two years, our community has been growing fast with more people joining us. It’s like a home full of blockchain enthusiasts who are learning, sharing, and exploring new knowledge together.

name: TokenPocket
statement: TokenPocket助力IOST生态发展，共同打造区块链未来。
statement_en: TokenPocket helps ecological development of IOST and jointly builds the future of blockchain.
description: TokenPocket 是一款支持多币种、多底层的通用数字钱包，融合了数字资产管理、交易、金融服务、资源租赁、投票表决、权限管理、账号管理、Dapp分发以及行情资讯等多种功能。TokenPocket致力于简化用户使用区块链的复杂度，服务于千千万万的DApp开发者，成为区块链数字世界的入口。
description_en: TokenPocket is a universal digital wallet that supports multi-chain and multi-currency. It combines digital asset management, trading, financial services, resource leasing, voting, permissions management, accounts management, Dapps distribution and market information. It is also feature-rich and can quickly find the services you need in different scenarios. TokenPocket is designed to simplify the complexity of blockchain for users, and serve thousands of DApp developers, making it the portal to blockchain digital worlds.

name: 哈佛肯尼迪政府学院区块链与数字货币协会
statement: 愿作公链校园生态引领者，推动校企共建共赢
statement_en: We are willing to be the leader of the public chain campus ecology and promote the co-construction and win-win of the university and the enterprise
description: 约翰·F·肯尼迪政府学院是世界顶尖的公共政策学校，也是美国哈佛大学的研究生院之一。学院可授公共政策、公共管理和国际发展等学位，也进行各种与政治和政府有关的研究。知名校友如联合国秘书长潘基文，世界银行行长罗伯特·佐利克，中国副总理刘鹤等。哈佛大学肯尼迪政府学院区块链与数字货币协会汇聚了哈佛校园内对区块链热衷的爱好且与波士顿大学、麻省理工学院等多校区块链学生社团组织拥有紧密联系，着眼于共建北美校园区块链生态，目前仅哈佛大学社区成员已逾百人
description_en: The John F. Kennedy School of Government is the world's leading public policy school and one of the graduate schools of Harvard University. The College offers degrees in public policy, public administration, and international development, as well as a variety of political and government-related research. Well-known alumni include UN Secretary-General Ban Ki-moon, World Bank President Robert Zoellick, Chinese Vice Premier Liu He and so on.Harvard Kennedy School Blockchain and Cryptocurrency PIC brings together Harvard's campus community's passion for blockchain and has close links with Boston University, MIT and other multi-campus student organizations of blockchain, with a view to build the economy of blockchain in North America. Only in Harvard, the member of the community is over 100.

name: 蜘蛛矿池
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: 蜘蛛矿池将整合多方资源，为IOST社区提供技术、资金支持，推动IOST生态健康发展。
statement_en: Zhizhu Pool will integrate all existing resources to provide full service regarding technology as well as needed capital for the growth of IOST community and ecology.
description: 蜘蛛矿池是专业的公有链节点服务商，获得了火币集团和节点资本的战略投资。拥有包括 eth 在内的多币种矿池，旗下eos节点 eoszhizhutop 排名节点前50名，有丰富的节点运营经验和社区资源。
description_en: Zhizhu Pool is a company specialized in public chain node service which is invested by Huobi Group and Node Capital. With rich node maintain experiences and community resources, and multi-cryptocurrency including ETH mine pool, Eoszhizhutop is now ranking top 50 among all EOS nodes.

name: My Century
statement: My Century自2017年开始涉足数字货币领域投资，IOST是公司最早投资的区块链公司之一。My Century 坚定看好IOST未来的发展前景，致力于IOST节点建设，协助IOST成为未来去中心化基础网络底层基础设施。
statement_en: My Century Partners invests on crypto-currencies since 2017 and IOST is the first blockchain portfolio of the company. My Century Partners will commited to the community building of IOST and help IOST to be the decentralized infrastrcture of blockchain.
description: My Century成立于2016年，是一家综合性的投资咨询公司，覆盖资产类别包含一二级市场TMT行业、数字货币、债券等，投资咨询团队有多年投资管理经验。
description_en: My Century Partners is a investment consultation company founded in 2016. My Century Partners invests on private equities, stocks and crypto-currencies. The management team have rich investment experience.

name: Cobo
statement: Cobo作为世界领先的钱包和数字资产管理公司，会在三条产品线，「Cobo钱包」，「Cobo金库」，「Cobo托管」上与IOST进行紧密合作，以优秀的产品回馈社区和服务用户。Cobo在超级节点管理方面已很成熟，稳定运行各类主链超级节点近千个。从产品形态和技术实力上都会是IOST节点竞选的优选伙伴.Cobo会为IOST用户建立社区，优先考虑将IOST DApp加入Cobo Wallet DApp生态。Cobo会为IOST社区生态管理设置专门的基金和Cobo生态内的项目孵化。
statement_en: Cobo is an organization that build leading crypto wallet and institutional crypto assets management solution. Cobo’s established three product lines - Cobo Wallet, Cobo Vaultand Cobo Custody - can be well integrated into IOST ecosystem. As a leading wallet company in the world to offer Proof-of-Stake (PoS) and Masternode rewards on user holdings, Cobo is experienced in managing up to thousands of Supernodes across multiple chains. I am confident Cobo will be an ideal candidate to become IOST Supernode candidate.Cobo will establish communities for IOST enthusiasts. We will also be prioritizing integrations and support for the IOST DApp ecosystem. We will look to set up a fund for IOST community management, project incubation and development related products within Cobo.
description: Cobo是全球第一家主打PoS和节点增益功能的数字货币钱包，希望通过努力，让用户“拥有和使用数字货币变得简单”。Cobo提供长期安全、可靠、便利的产品和服务 。Cobo的产品线包括面向初级用户的「Cobo钱包」，面向高端用户的冷存储产品「Cobo金库」以及未来即将上线的面向机构投资者的「Cobo托管」。Cobo支持30多种主流币种、500多种代币，并汇聚优质DAPP，我们致力于提供一站式数字货币服务。
description_en: Cobo is the first leading wallet company in the world to offer Proof-of-Stake (PoS) and masternode rewards on user holdings, making it easy for users to grow their digital assets effortlessly.As a company, we emphasize long-term security, reliability, and convenience. Our key products and services reflect that vision. Altogether, Cobo offers a secure mobile wallet (Cobo Wallet), high-end cold storage wallet for advanced users (Cobo Vault), and custodial services for institutional investors (Cobo Custody).With support for over thirty different coins, 500 tokens, and an integrated DApp store along the way, we aim to be a one-stop shop for everything crypto.

name: IOST Game
statement: IOST区块链网络让玩家的权利、义务以及收益集中在一个游戏生态中，为IOST用户创造一个基于游戏内容的共识社区。IOST Game团队是一个具备正直价值观和超强执行力的团队，我们真诚希望通过IOST节点能为IOST生态和用户带来更多乐趣。
statement_en: The IOST blockchain network enables players to realize their rights, obligations and benefits in one gaming ecosystem, helping develop a community consensuses based on game content. We sincerely hope that by being one of the IOST nodes, we can bring more fun for IOST users and the IOST ecosystem.
description: IOST Game旨在将区块链的分布式账本技术应用到游戏娱乐中，将用户需求、游戏内容与区块链技术进行融合，通过挖掘和调研IOST社区内游戏玩家的游戏偏好，提供好玩、有趣的游戏产品，并通过特定游戏玩法和游戏内容创作工具，帮助玩家深度参与到游戏的发展中，无论你擅长美术设计，游戏策划，代码编程还是经济学研究，都可以一块创作游戏，成就你的游戏天赋和价值。
description_en: By applying blockchain technology to the gaming industry, IOST Game aims to provide more fun and interesting game products where players are encouraged to create their own content and get more involved in game development under specific gameplays and with the help of related development kits. No matter if you are good at UI design, story telling, programming or economics, you will always be able to find a place to contribute your effort and realize your value in the creation of the games.

name: 飞天小猪
statement: 齐心协力，让IOST走进千家万户。
statement_en: Let us work together and get more people to know IOST!
description: 大家好，我是一名IOST的死忠粉。我个人是一名中科院的博士生，从事着自人工智能方面的研究。去年因为朋友的关系接触到了IOST，被其设计理念以及远大抱负所吸引。我虽然不是什么大户，但是我希望尽自己的绵薄之力来帮助IOST社区进行推广，能够让尽可能多的人认识IOST的技术，这可能也是去中心化的一个初衷吧。我也非常希望能看到IOST未来更多的出现一些落地的应用，在此之前我愿意同IOST一起成长一起进步，希望广大IOST的粉丝们能够多多支持我。
description_en: Hello, I’m Zhu Junnan, a follower of IOST. I am also a doctor in the Chinese Academy of Sciences and focuses on the research on natural language processing. I got to know about IOST last year through my friend. I was really inspired by IOST’s design concept and high ambition. Though I am not a big holder of IOST but still strongly wish to contribute to IOST community building and get more people to know about IOST, which also embodies the decentralized concept of the blockchain. Besides, I’m looking forward to seeing more IOST’s real use cases in the future. I’m willing to make progress with IOST. Please vote for me!

name: IOSTABC
statement: 把为IOST生态的健康发展做贡献作为目标和使命，做社区最专业可靠的数据服务提供者。
statement_en: Our mission is that making contribution to the healthy development of IOST ecosystem, and becoming the more professional and dependable data service provider.
description: IOSTABC团队由一群对区块链有着狂热爱好的极客组成。团队成员超过三分之二是技术人员，除此外还有高效精悍的产品运营团队，从各个方面保证IOSTABC战斗力，做好长期为IOST社区服务的准备。我们对新兴事物有着强烈的好奇心，并且坚信通过创新能够极大的优化现有机制提升社会组织效率，我们爱钻研不怕折腾，核心人员在区块链领域研究深入且颇有心得。我们因相信区块链未来而聚在一起，既希望尽绵薄之力支持IOST生态的长期发展，也希望帮助投资者和用户获得更多的收益。
description_en: IOSTABC team is a geek group who has a huge interest of blockchain. We have prepared to serve for the IOST community, because we own an excellent technical team and a great operation team. We have a strong curiosity to fresh object, and we believe we can optimize existing mechanism to improve the efficiency of community by innovation. In addition, we never fear the difficulties, our core members did an in-depth research in the field of Blockchain. The belif of Blockchain future makes us come together. We hope we will try our best to support the long-term development of IOST ecosystem, and help the investors and users to obtain more income.

name: IOST. TUZI
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: 区块链是伟大的，它是继蒸汽机、发电机、互联网之后又一变革性的创新。IOST是这次变革中改变世界的项目之一。它是一个创新、安全的区块链技术，为线上虚拟服务以及数字货品交换提供一个高可扩容、高吞吐的生态环境。我要陪伴着IOST一起成长。
statement_en: Blockchain is great. It is another innovative innovation after steam engine, generator and internet. IOST is one of the world-changing projects in this transformation. It is an innovative and secure block chain technology, providing a high scalable and high throughput ecological environment for online virtual services and digital goods exchange. I want to grow up with IOST
description: 本节点是个人竞选，不是什么社区也不是什么机构。我之所以要竞选是因为自接触到IOST竞选节点后，知道每个人都可以竞选，那我就想试试。
description_en: This node is an individual campaign, not a community or an institution. I want to run because I know that everyone can run when I get to the IOST campaign node, so I want to try.

name: 天之乐游戏
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: “爱生活，爱棋牌”已经越来越多的成为广大玩家的一种生活态度！展望未来，我们将专注于IOST公链上研发地方特色游戏，为广大玩家提供更好、更公平的游戏产品！为IOST发展贡献力量！
statement_en: Love life, love chess and CARDS has more and more become a general player's attitude towards life! Looking into the future, we will focus on IOST public chain research and development of local characteristics of the game, to provide better and more fair game products for the majority of players! Contribute to IOST development!
description: 天之乐是一家运营地方特色棋牌的游戏公司，凭借雄厚的技术实力、极富新意的游戏设计能力及独特的竞技组合比赛模式，已在市场上形成了强大的竞争力，在玩家和合作商中累积了良好口碑。
description_en: Tianzhille is a game company which operates local chess and cards. With its strong technical strength, innovative game design ability and unique competitive combination competition mode, Tianzhille has formed a strong competitiveness in the market, and has accumulated a good reputation among players and partners.

name: 火蓝服务
statement: 火蓝坚信IOST能快速发展，我们共同为IOST社区服务，把所有节点奖励都分给社区贡献者，共同为IOST发展做出贡献和努力！
statement_en: HuoLan firmly believes IOST is on a fast track. Let us work together to contribute to IOST community building and distribute all the rewards to the community.
description: 火蓝服务成立于2017年初，在区块链行业已拥有二年推广经验，火蓝服务分为两个版块。一、火蓝刀锋推广团队，团队现有近百人推广队伍，做事严谨，注重效率，拥有上万微信社群，上千telegramqq群资源，为近百项目做为策划，推广方案，根据项目制定出适合的推广方案，方案多样化，是项目方打开市场的一把尖刀！二、链评天下（自媒体），链评天下已入驻"bishijie":  核财经，币快报，币车，向北财经，"币乎":  烯财经，今日头条等各大财经，配合项目方发布一些文章。
description_en: HuoLan Service was founded in early 2017, and have two years of experience in the promotion. HuoLan Service currently focuses on 2 businesses: The first part is the marketing team which are comprised of nearly 100 people who are rigorous, highly effective people. They have successfully built thousands of WeChat groups and hundreds of Telegram and QQ groups. We have done customized planning and promotion for more than 100 projects. The second part is Lian Ping Tian Xia, a we-media platform, which has been present in various media platforms such as CoinNess, He Finance, Bi Kuai Bao, Bi Che, Xiang Bei Finance, Bi Hu, Xi Finance, Toutiao Today. We have published many articles for blockchain projects.

name: 劲草节点
statement: 集天下英才，聚天下财富，做未来创举，成千秋大业。
statement_en: Gather all the talents and fortunes to do big things. Dream wildly and make it come true.
description: 道哥，职业独立投资人，2008年正式接触股市和外汇，从此踏入投资行业的漫漫长路，一路摸爬滚打到了2019年，有幸成为IOST节点合伙人。
description_en: Hi, you can call me Brother Dao, and I’m an independent professional investor. I began to know about the stock exchange and foreign reserve starting in 2008 and have been dealing with investment businesses ever since. I feel very honored to be an IOST Partner Candidate.

name: DappPub
statement: 释放去中心化应用的无限可能 -- DappPub
statement_en: Unleashing the power of DApps!
description: DappPub开发团队目前深耕区块链DApp生态相关协议及解决方案的构建，希望借助区块链技术以『释放DApp的无限可能』。公司现注册在新加坡，成员主要来自国内原一线互联网公司。团队具有丰富的公链DApp开发经验（EOS, NAS），曾推出多款知名区块链生态协议及解决方案，同时也具备运营EOS节点、用户社群、开发者社区的相关经验。
description_en: The DappPub development team aims to “unleash the power of DApps” and has been engaged in building blockchain powered protocols and solutions for the DApp ecosystem. The company is registered in Singapore and its core members mainly come from top tier Chinese IT companies. The team has rich DApp development experience on permission-less chains (EOS, NAS) and has published a series of well-known protocols and solutions for the DApp ecosystem. DappPub also has related experience in the operation of EOS nodes, user communities and developer communities as well.

name: 必胜
statement: 为了IOST将来更好，大家一起努力！
statement_en: Let us work together to make IOST better!
description:
大家好我是小安。
我来自河南郑州，我是一名实业接班人，现在主要经营的是电动机，搅拌站，搅拌机，环保设备
从小生活在富裕家庭里，我的性格偏于内向，为人坦率、热情、讲求原则；处事乐观、专心、细致、头脑清醒；富有责任心、乐于助人。
description_en: Hello, I’m Xiao An from Zheng Zhou, He Nan Province. IOST is the next-generation blockchain technology which I believe will transform our lives in the future, and that is also the reason I wish to do something for IOST and the Zero-Barrier Partner Election Program gives me this chance though I am not a tech person. Support me and let us build IOST together!

name: Rasky
statement: 近几年区块链的火热发展，受到了广大网民关注及热捧，然而2018年是前所未有低潮期，尽管如此，我们看到IOST的研发团队依旧踏实做事，毫不动摇，默默奉献令我们感到暖心和安心，我们也将继续加大持有量，并支持配合IOST在今后发展的道路上不断前进，当然TOKEN的价值是整个IOST价值的体现，也是投资者获得回报的关键，我们看好IOST未来的前景，争取做第一公链，所以请各位志同道合朋友加入我们吧！
statement_en: Blockchain technology has been gaining traction among the public. Despite the adverse market conditions in 2018, we are deeply encouraged by IOST’s down-to-earth approach and unremitted efforts in their development process. We will support IOST all the way through and believe that IOST is destined to be the first blockchain platform! Join us to build a better IOST!
description: Rasky是以IOST爱好者个人发起的组织。
description_en: Rasky is an association initiated by IOST enthusiasts.

name: TEAM Joy
statement: 为IOST生态源源不断地提供优质的游戏内容。
statement_en: Providing quality games to IOST ecosystem continuously.
description: Team Joy 是Joy系列游戏平台的开发维护团队，旗下拥有全球首个区块链休闲竞技平台。团队成员拥有丰富的“区块链+游戏”经验，在产品运营、游戏设计、智能合约等各个方向都具有深入洞察及实践。Team Joy 致力于推动区块链游戏的普及和拓展，推出精品爆款区块链休闲竞技游戏。Team Joy是区块链游戏的引领者和开拓者，这是我们全球顶级区块链游戏开发团队不可推卸的责任。
description_en: Team Joy is the development team of the platform for Joy series games and owns the world's first blockchain light sport platform. The team members have extensive experience in blockchain+games”, as well as deep insights and practices in product operations, game design and smart contracts. Team Joy 's mission is to promote the popularization and expansion of blockchain games, and produce excellent & hot blockchain-based light sports games, which is the duty Team Joy, as a world top blockchain game developing team is committed dedicated to.

name: 杭州仙女座科技
statement: 仙女座科技节点希望利用自己的热情和专业技能来为IOST区块链应用开发者赋能，推动IOST的发展。
statement_en: The Andromeda Technology Node hopes to use our enthusiasm and expertise to empower the developers of IOST blockchain and promote the development of IOST.
description:
2018 年是 Dapp 的元年，2019 年则是公链竞争最激烈的一年。这一年我们相信，得开发者得天下。仙女座科技 IOST 节点是一群热爱分享且有热情的 DApp 开发者组建的，旨在普及智能合约开发的相关实践知识，定期提供一整套合约开发的范例。我们深耕 DAPP 及合约开发，目标成为公链平台上最强的第三方。团队从 17 年开始陆续发布 Dapp 作品，目前已在多个公链上自研并移植了多款成功的 Dapp 作品，获得过多次 Dapp 激励计划的奖项，并在实践的基础上总结并设计了 Kyubey Dapp 孵化器通证协议，并获得了第一届分布式资本通证经济设计大赛第一名。 
仙女座科技节点创始人唐飞虎曾连续4届获 ACM/ICPC 金牌，并获得 2015 年微软编程之美冠军，Gpool 联合创始人，在 Google 任职期间，曾成立区块链学习小组。
description_en:
2018 is the year of DApp, and 2019 is the most competitive year for the public blockchain. We believe the blockchain with the most top developers will win in the competition in this year. Andoromeda IOST Node formed by a group of passionate DApp developers, aiming to popularize the knowledge of smart contract development and will provide a series of smart contract template examples on a regular basis. Deeply involved in DApp and smart contract development, we define our vision to become the most powerful 3rd party on the public blockchain ecosystem. We successfully released a variety of DApps since 2017 on different public blockchains and won the DApp incentive competition for several times. We summarized our practical experiences and designed a token offering protocol which won the 1st prize on the 1st TEDC token economic competition of Fenbushi Capital.
Feihu Tang, the founder of Andromeda Technology Node, won the ACM/ICPC Gold Medal for four consecutive years and won the 2015 Microsoft Programming Beauty Champion, the co-founder of Gpool, and established a blockchain study group during his employment at Google.

name: AiyaaNet
statement:
AiyaaNetは中華圏（中国本土・香港・台湾）の最新情報を日本国内へと紹介するブログメディアです。
昨今の中華圏の変化のスピードはとても早く、日本国内にはその実情が伝わっていません。
AiyaaNetではIT・金融・エンタメの3本軸で中華圏の最新動向を分かりやすく解説します。
IOST票の獲得のために、AiyaaNetは良質な記事を定期的に発信します。
そして、ブロックチェーンの最先端を担う、中華圏の情報を正確にかつ適切な解説でお届けすることを約束します。
AiyaaNet運営は日本在住の中国人・香港人・台湾人のネットワークを最大限に活用し、IOSTの普及と票の獲得を目指します。
statement_en: AIYAA helps general users to use IOST easily by organizing published all information about IOST ecosystem into readable. We provide a one-stop-website allows multilingual users to freely access information on nodes, Wallets, Exchanges and DApps from PCs, smartphones, and other devices.
description:
AiyaaNetはまだ始まったばかりのブログメディアですが、
個々のメンバーは中華圏出身または渡航経験もあり知識に富んでいます。
また、IT、金融、エンタメそれぞれの知見が深いメンバーが揃っており、発信される情報の質を高めることに余念がありません。
AiyaaNet運営は2019年夏までに日本における中国情報発信ブログメディアとして、TOP3に位置することを目指します。
description_en: AIYAA is a general information website of IOST for Japanese community. We focus on IOST projects and with our strict policy, we do not accept any advertisements in the token economy (vote). In the near future, we integrate IOST smart contracts into this website.

name: IOST World
statement: IOST World is trying to lead the Korean pool as the center of the role. Although Korea is the largest market in the world for the cryptocurrency market, its weakness is that it does not have a team to represent yet. But that's one of the biggest strengths for us, and we're going to bring together numerous holders that you would like to participate in the configuration of the nodes, we will build a top-level ecosystem within the IOST nodes around the world. IOST World는 역할의 중심축이 되어 한국의 풀을 선도해 나가려고 합니다. 한국은 전세계 암호화폐 시장 중 가장 큰 시장이지만, 아직은 대표할 팀이 없다는 것이 약점입니다. 하지만 이 점은 우리에게 가장 큰 강점으로, 노드 구성에 참여하고 싶은 수많은 홀더들을 규합하여 전세계의 IOST 노드 내에서도 최상위 규모의 생태계를 건설할 것입니다.

name: 深圳市星际大陆科技有限公司
statement: 星际大陆致力于推动分布式存储协议的全球化应用，让数据存储更安全，让数据所有权回归你我。
statement_en: IPFSMAIN is committed to promoting the global application of distributed storage protocols, making data storage more secure, and returning data ownership to you and me.
description:
IPFSMAIN星际大陆是坚定的IPFS生态建设者、 去中心化存储践行者，致力于为用户提供存储矿机研 发生产、矿场建设托管、矿池软件开发、应用开发等服务。 
星际大陆地处深圳--全球硬件之都，拥有成熟 完整的产业供应链，技术团队由原金蝶产品总监、创维存储服务部门总监、中兴研发负责人、华为资深存 储工程师等互联网巨头高管组成，5月份获华迎基金 3000万天使轮投资，矿机获得深圳宝安十大精品奖，公司获得硅谷商学院颁发“全球区块链企业之星”奖。 
星际大陆坚持“真诚到永远•专业到极致”的为人做事理念，为构建信息自由的新世界而努力，让网络的自由和独立精神充分发挥，持续为客户创造价值。
description_en: IPFSMain has 20 core team members, they graduated from the top universities in China, most of them have graduate degree and overseas education background. Our backbones have served well-known companies many years and also have built mining farm experience. We already built community in Europe, North America and Asia. IPFSMain hope we can help community sharing resources, provide a platform for interaction. Make IPFS community stronger and better.

name: D.STREET
statement:
사람들의 신뢰를 기반으로 하는 매일경제 및 디스트리트 플랫폼들을 통해 IOST를 더 많은 사람들에게 알리고 커뮤니케이션 할 수 있습니다. 
그럼으로써 더 많은 개발자들이 관심을 갖게 할 수 있으며, 유저를 확대하고, IOST 브랜드를 강화하는데 큰 도움이 될 것입니다.

description:
D.STREET(디스트리트)는 블록체인 전문 엑셀러레이터 '블록크래프터스'와 대한민국 1위 경제미디어 '매일경제' 그리고 '데일리 금융그룹' 이렇게 3사가 투자하여 설립한 합작 법인입니다. 
정체되고 혼탁한 블록체인 커뮤니티에서 한 줄기 빛과 같은 존재가 되기 위해 노력하고 있으며, 믿을 수 있는 블록체인 뉴스와 커뮤니티 플랫폼(웹, 앱) 역시 제공합니다. 
디스트리트 내 속해 있는 국내 TOP 인플루언서들과 매일경제의 뉴스기사/PR, 디스트리트의 페이스북, 유튜브 채널, 디스트리트 자체 웹/앱 플랫폼을 통해 IOST를 더 많은 사람에게 알리고 토큰 홀더로부터 Vote를 이끌어 낼 수 있습니다.

name: Nova wallet
statement:

We’d like to continue our victory saga into the English world, which bears a vision to become the most influential information provider for the blockchain and crypto world.

Support our vision and work with developing Guestking with backing our candidacy to host a IOST Node with your possible IOST Token Votes. We believe IOST will deliver. Every time. For all users & services of the future. Guestking will assist making IOST the first choice to any transaction. So, everyone, please. Get involved already today. Get your IOST tokens ready and use your voting power to support the Guestking Node Candidacy and help us lead the future for any guest to use IOST during any visit to any location in the future. Hence, thanks ever so much to all possible votes for the Guestking Node Candidacy in the upcoming Node #election that start mid-January 2019 and lasts until IOST MainNet launch in February. With its services, support the practical experience, principally designed for any guest visit. Including payment. name: Sutler Ventures
statement: Sutler Ventures (SV) 致力于推动去中心化技术和社区的应用落地。Sutler Ventures支持在社会，商业，和社区建设上具有强烈价值观和理念的项目，这也是我们为什么支持IOST的原因Sutler Ventures认为IOST一直致力于成为新兴的去中心化商业和网络的引领着。IOST团队开发了一项具有根本价值的技术，并建立了一直推动IOST建设的社区。立足于实现目标的技术和活跃社区的有效融合必将推动IOST的持续发展。Sutler Ventures 将积极推动IOST网络的参与者的发展，尤其是对IOST的网络和社区有巨大推动潜力的第三方业务和去中心化应用。Sutler Ventures 是IOST生态的早期投资者，积极帮助IOST宣传和募资，并帮助IOST联合创建项目。Sutler Ventures将积极支持符合IOST愿景和投资框架的网络参与者提供资金，意见，营销等更多方面的支持。最后，Sutler Ventures将积极发放奖励回馈为Sutler Ventures投票 的社群。请浏览我们的网站以获取更多关于投票奖励的信息。
statement_en:
Sutler Ventures (SV) aims to accelerate the adoption of decentralized technologies and communities. SV looks to support projects with strong values and belief around the power of a decentralized framework in society, business, community and more who plan on building on IOST. SV believes that the vision from the IOST team has positioned IOST to become a leading participant in new decentralized businesses and networks. The IOST team has developed technology that is fundamentally valuable and a community that is actively engaged in the success of the IOST network. This combination of purposeful technology and proactive community growth will help the IOST network to grow. 

Sutler Ventures will focus strictly on the growth of IOST network participants, primarily third-party businesses and decentralized applications, that show very strong potential to benefit the overall IOST network and community. The SV team has invested significantly in the IOST ecosystem already, and assisted in marketing and fundraising for IOST and its co-founded projects. SV will provide funding, insight, marketing and more to the IOST network participants who fit the SV vision and framework for investment. 

Finally, SV will give back to the community through an active reward process to those who vote for the SV node, meeting the required IOST voting reward structure. Please visit our website for more information on voting rewards.
description: Sutler Ventures拥有一只加密行业的精英团队，团队成员具有在软件开打，金融管理和交易的经验，并且多人曾经在 加密公司ICO Alert任职，在商业开发，咨询，募资和营销有广泛的经验。整个SV团队期待通过Sutler Ventures的管理来支持IOST生态系统!
description_en:
Sutler Ventures was created by talented cryptocurrency industry members who's previous experience includes software development, financial management and trading, various positions at the cryptocurrency company ICO Alert, business development, consulting, fundraising and marketing. 

The entire SV team is looking forward to supporting the IOST ecosystem through the management of Sutler Ventures!

name: OEX
statement: 我们将全力让那些尚未决定在哪个区块链平台搭建应用，并需要建立一个去中心化经济机制的项目首选IOST平台！
statement_en: We will let projects that have not decided on TPS blockchain infrastructure and in need for a decentralized economy to choose IOST as our first choice.
description: OEX国际私人有限公司成立于2017年，总部设在新加坡。OEX (www.oex.com)是世界一流的数字资产交易平台之一，为全球用户提供交易BTC、ETH等多种数字资产的平台，并支持BTC、ETH等交易渠道。OEX获得了众多著名奖项，其中最著名的是“2017年和2018年区块链特别贡献奖”。在技术指标、产品线、价值管理、运营、客户服务体系等方面，OEX一直在区块链行业领先，也因此吸引了许多高价值项目加入了我们。OEX始终坚持“安全第一、用户至上、无欺诈、无不道德行为”的原则，为用户提供服务和帮助。目前，全球已有50多个国家采用了我们的平台，这个数字还在不断增长。
description_en:
OEX International Private Limited was established in 2017, with its headquarter in Singapore. OEX (www.oex.com) is one of the World-Class Digital Asset Exchange, providing global users a platform to trade a wide range of digital assets such as BTC and ETH, as well as supporting BTC, ETH and other trading channels. OEX received numerous prestigious awards, notably “The Special Contribution Award in Blockchain in 2017 & 2018”.

In terms of technical indicators, product lines, value management, operations and customer service systems, OEX has been leading the blockchain industry. Thus attracting many high valued projects. 

OEX consistently adheres to the principle of “safety first, user first, no fraud and no unethical behavior”, to service and assist our users. Currently, up to 50 countries around the world have adopted our platform and the number is increasing.

OEX is committed to explore more profitable and mutual-beneficial activities, hence enhancing user experience and delivering better investing opportunities to our global users. 

We strongly welcome feedback and encourage more participation of high quality project initiatives to bring us to new heights.

name: Rate3 Network
statement:
在Rate3跨链协议加持下，任何人都可以轻松地在各个区块链上发行可进行资产交换的通证，创
建跨链、可自我管理的身份信息，并以此为基础构筑如共享信誉系统等各种使用场景。
除了以太坊和恒星网以外，IOST将成为第三个Rate3跨链协议所支持的区块链。这些区块链能够 通过互操作性而迅速增长。这也同时降低了集成多个区块链的产品的开发难度。我们的稳定币 SGDR是一个非常实际的用例，它的诞生使IOST、恒星网和以太坊的用户可以无需顾忌钱包不兼 容的问题，轻松地进行跨链转账支付。
团队希望能将IOST生态系统所提供的便捷带给双方现有的活跃社区(Twitter和telegram的两万多位 用户)，和整个东南亚的区块链市场。
statement_en:
Rate3 will share with its 20k+ strong Telegram community and our 25k+ Twitter followers on the key pillars of how we will add value to the IOST ecosystem. 

Technology & Business
Rate3’s value proposition lies in the fact that any organization or entity leveraging upon it can create tokens (utility tokens, stablecoins, asset-backed tokens, securities, etc) and move these tokens across multiple supported blockchains. In addition, they will also be able to create cross-chain, self-sovereign identities, thus unlocking use cases such as shared reputation systems and decentralized federation systems, among others. 

IOST will be supported on Rate3’s cross-chain protocol for tokenization and identity management alongside with Ethereum and Stellar. This will allow the network effects of all these interoperable blockchains to grow exponentially, where products may be constructed out of integrations to various Dapps from seperate blockchains. Our stablecoin will be a prime example of this, as users of each of the different chains will be able to seamlessly transfer payments among each other. 

Having already established strong relationships with licensed and reputable legal and custodian partners in Singapore, Rate3 can also help IOST gain a good initial foothold on the security token space, thus enabling potential STO issuers to conduct their security token offering here in Singapore on top of the IOST platform.

Community
Rate3 has a highly engaged and active international community. We will host regular quarterly meetups in Singapore - and schedule-permitting, Southeast Asia as well - introducing new community members to IOST to drive awareness and adoption.

Education & Research 
With past research pieces having been picked up by publications such as Hackernoon, FreeCodeCamp and Good Audience, the team has displayed a keen eye for research and a flair for writing on all things blockchain and tokenization. We will continue with generating additional content to help educate the public around IOST’s high-throughput blockchain.
description: Rate3 Network 是一个跨链通证化和身份管理的协议。借助他们的双协议，Rate3成功推出了以新 加坡元为支撑的稳定币——​SGDR​。自2016年成立以来，其背后团队也同时在运营一家发展迅速 的金融科技创业公司，名为RateX。
description_en:
Rate3 Network is a cross-chain asset tokenization protocol. The team has a strong track record in running a high growth fintech startup business called RateX since its incorporation in 2016. Rate3 Network is the infrastructural technology that underpinned the launch of SGDR, a Singapore-dollar backed stablecoin issued based off tokenizing fully collateralized fiat money.

Through a close partnership with IOST, the Rate3 team will be leveraging their prior experience with SGDR to initially launch a cross-chain stablecoin for seamless, low volatility value transfers across users and Dapps on both the IOST and Ethereum ecosystems. This will greatly reduce the friction for the existing Ethereum network user base to explore using Dapps on IOST. This capability will also be extended to allow for cross-chain swaps for all other tokens (aside from stablecoins) as well in future.

Such close alignment of incentives to secure the IOST network ensures that Rate3 will uphold its responsibilities as a node validator to the highest degree if selected.

As a blockchain evangelist, she keeps a close watch on IOST and is particularly interested in the vision and commitment shown by the IOST team even during a bear market, and is excited to spread IOST's vision of an inclusive ecosystem with her network and community.

name: Metanyx
statement: Metanyx 将在IOST网络运行高可靠的Servi节点推动IOST生态的发展，Metanyx 将努力保证区块的有效生产。Metanyx背后的团队从一开始就参与了IOST社区，包括在官方的IOST存储库中提出一些有史以来的第一个问题，并积极支持Reddit上的IOST网络。Metanyx提供了与运行完整节点相关的文档贡献，并将在未来围绕Dapp开发继续提供更多的贡献。Metanyx将在未来推出mainnet时向IOST网络引入其他业务，届时将为我们的投票者提供额外的奖励。
statement_en: Metanyx will support the IOST ecosystem by running a high availability Servi on the IOST network to ensure blocks are produced whenever requested.The team behind Metanyx has been involved in IOST community from the beginning including raising some of the first ever issues within the official IOST repository as well as actively supporting the IOST network on Reddit. Metanyx has provided documentation contributions in relation to running a full node and will continue to make further contributions in the future around Dapp development.Metanyx will introduce other businesses to the IOST network in the future when the mainnet launches which will provide voters with additional rewards.
description: Metanyx是一个技术经验丰富的企业家组成的团队，并成功地多个行业建立了业务。Metanyx团队参与了金融、法律和数字货币等行业的高交易平台的构建和设计。
description_en: Metanyx are a team of highly technical entrepreneurs with a variety of successful businesses across multiple industries. The team behind Metanyx have been directly involved in building and designing highly transactional platforms in the financial, legal and digital signage industries.

name: IOST Americas
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: 凭借多年运行专用服务器、为其他项目生产区块的经验，和对金融市场的了解，相信我们的团队将运行在IOST生态系统中最透明、最可靠的节点。未来我们将会举办各种meetup活动，建立一个专业的开发者网络来回馈IOST生态系统。我们不会以虚拟人物和假名字欺骗投票者。透明性，社区和信任是我们最珍重的价值。
statement_en: We are committed to training #devs for the IOST network and implementing blockchain projects on IOST for clients.
description: IOST Americas是一个由连续技术创业者组成的区块链布道群，我们致力于支持和开发优秀的区块链项目。此外，我们也是一家专注于区块链技术，人工智能（AI）和物联网（IOT）的咨询公司。我们将为IOST网络培训相关的开发人员，并在IOST上执行客户的区块链项目。
description_en: IOST Americas is a blockchain evangelical group of serial tech entrepreneurs. We are committed to supporting and developing amazing blockchain projects. We are also an R&D consulting company focusing on #blockchain, #AI & #IoT. We are committed to training #devs for the IOST network and implementing blockchain projects on IOST for clients.

name: IOSTer Korea
statement: 한국에서 IOST 생태계가 확실히 자리잡고 성장할 수 있도록 블록체인 커뮤니티에 IOST의 장점을 확실히 알리고 공감받을 수 있도록 하겠습니다
statement_en: 한국에서 IOST 생태계가 확실히 자리잡고 성장할 수 있도록 블록체인 커뮤니티에 IOST의 장점을 확실히 알리고 공감받을 수 있도록 하겠습니다
description: 한국에 수많은 해외 유망 프로젝트를 소개한 블록체인 커뮤니티 입니다.
description_en: 한국에 수많은 해외 유망 프로젝트를 소개한 블록체인 커뮤니티 입니다.

name: Attic Lab IOST
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: 我们致力于在建设IOST的生态建设中发挥首要作用。为此，我们在智能合约开发，管理和宣传IOST等方面支持IOST的发展。作为一个产品公司，我们也将继续推动IOST区块链技术早日实现落地应用。我们的所有代码将在 Github上公开，以方便测试和应用。任何深刻的变革离不开人们对其背后理念的支持。很多人现在尚未理解IOST背后的核心理念，相信我们将会在传播IOST价值方面将发挥重要作用。我们将努力为IOST的持有者，开发者，潜在的Servi Nodes和有意向买IOST的朋友解释IOST的设计理念和如何安全使用IOST网络。我们将开发，生产一些IOST的资料，并利用各种工具和渠道向大众传播。
statement_en:
We envision our primary role as facilitation in enhancing IOST ecosystem. For that, we will dedicate our efforts to smart contract development, governance, and promotion of IOST. As a product company, we are planning to continue our research on use cases of IOST underlying blockchain and our products. All the code will be publicly available through Github repositories for testing purposes and subsequent utilization.

At the heart of any significant change lies an idea that people embrace. As it might be difficult to grasp the core concepts quickly behind IOST, education is an inevitable part of our marketing strategy. We aim to explain token holders, developers, potential Servi Nodes, and soon-to-be token holders how the network is designed and how to utilize it safely. Attic Lab will create, produce, and distribute its educational materials across devices and channels.
description: Attic Lab是区块链领域的软件开发公司。我们的团队来自Kyiv，乌克兰，团队成员都是一群精通技术的区块链开发者和爱好者。Attic Lab成立于2016年，我们的业务由提供用户所需的区块链解决方案成功转入产品业务。
description_en: Attic Lab is a software development company operating in the blockchain industry. Our team of tech-savvy blockchain developers and enthusiasts locates in Kyiv, Ukraine. Founded in 2016, Attic Lab has gone through a long process of transitioning from a company dealing in tailor-made blockchain software solutions to a product firm.

name: Hashed.Asia
statement: 1.将在我们的网站上更新IOST的发展动态以传播给用户。 2.作为IOST在亚洲拓展业务的交流渠道。 3.我们正在建立奖励的网页，IOST dapps可以利用我们的奖励页面发起ICO奖励。 4.如果IOST可以提供一些数据或代码，我们可以建立一个dapp跟踪页面展示IOST dapps，并邀请用户使用 IOST dapps
statement_en:
1) Share news of all IOST developments on our website to help educate users.
2) Be a communication channel for IOST to reach out to Asia (ex-China) region.
3) In process of setting up bounties page. IOST dapps can launch ICO bounties on our page.
4) If IOST help to provide data and maybe some code, we can set up a dapp tracker page to showcase IOST dapps and refer in users to IOST dapps.
description: https://hashed.asia是亚洲领先的数字货币新闻网站，报道主体语言为英语，并翻译为6种亚洲语言。运用亚洲有多元的文化和语言，https://hashed.asia用本土化的方式向用户提供前沿新闻，价格，分析，和专家意见等。https://hashed.asia的使命是向传递新闻，联系和教育亚洲社群，成为最权威的每日新闻来源。
description_en: https://hashed.asia is the leading Asian crypto news website with global coverage in English and translations into six major Asian languages. With Asia's rich cultural and language diversity, Hashed.Asia is uniquely positioned to offer our audience the latest news, prices, analysis and expert opinions in localized content. Hashed.Asia's mission is to inform, educate and connect the Asian community as the authoritative daily news source.

name: 安融区块
statement: 安融区块将通过自身社区以及媒体专栏持续不断推进IOST生态建设，安融区块愿同IOST共同成长。
statement_en: The Anrong block will continue to promote iost ecological construction through its own community and media columns. The Anrong block is willing to grow with IOST.
description: 安融区块是一个区块链投资社区，目前社区有币圈精准人群6000+ 业务涵盖区块链投资、挖矿、社区建设。安融区块致力于区块链行业数据挖掘分析，给社区人员提供最有价值的投资报告。
description_en: The Anrong block is a blockchain investment community. At present, the community has a precise circle of 6000+ business covering blockchain investment, mining, and community building. The Anrong block is dedicated to data mining analysis in the blockchain industry, providing community members with the most valuable investment reports.

name: 黑曜石实验室
statement: 我们的团队拥有强大的技术储备和丰富的产品经验，希望能够提供给IOST上的开发者和用户更高效的开发环境和更好的产品体验。
statement_en: Our team has strong technology reserve and rich product design experience. We hope to provide IOST developers and users a more efficient develop environment and better product experience.
description: IOST Obsidian是来自美国旧金山的开发团队，专注于为去中心化应用生态提供技术支持和企业级软件产品。我们的项目涉及基础设施、开发者工具、跨链钱包、以及去中心化的应用程序等。
description_en: IOST Obsidian is a technology studio from San Francisco, focusing on technical support and enterprise-level products for the decentralized application ecosystem. Our projects include infrastructure solutions, developer tools, multi-chain wallet, and decentralized applications.

name: IOST ZhangYi
statement: 将拥护IOST的理念，维护IOST的权益，建设稳定安全共享收益的节点生态，加入我们，一同迎接区块链春天的到来！
statement_en: We believe in IOST’s core idea, safeguards the rights of IOST, and strives to build a stable, healthy and secure ecosystem where everybody wins. Join us to welcome the arrival of spring of blockchain technology!
description: 区块链知名投资人，比特币华中地区布道者，2014年开始参与比特币投资，国内知名项目小蚁量子链早期投资人。
description_en: A veteran blockchain investor and Bitcoin evangelist in central China. Having invested in Bitcoin since 2014, I am also an early investor in well-known domestic blockchain projects such as NEO and Qtum.

name: 链金术
statement: 链金术将全力打造IOST生态交互社区，为构建新形态的社会模式不断的探索完善。成员自由平等，社群公开透明，无中心化统治，高度自治自运转，有序公平。
statement_en: Lianjinshu is dedicated to building a worldwide interactive community that is based on IOST ecological chain, with ongoing efforts to explore and search for a new social formation. We believe all members are equal and free in this community. We aim to build a free and equal community that upholds openness and transparency, and a decentralized and highly autonomous environment that provides order and equity for all members.
description:
链金术（lianjinshu.com）-区块链资讯平台。 自2018年初上线以来，着力打造中国一流的区块链社区，以推进区块链行业的发展与进步。
2018年5月 链金术参与波场TRON SR竞选并当选至今。
参与EOS主网全球声名并助力EOS主网安全测试。
2018年6月 链金术线下活动开启。
2018年7月 链金术每周线上活动开启。
2018年8月 链金术KOL大V原创文章大范围发声，引领DAPP圈。
2018年9月 链金术音频节目《十点区块链》上线。
2018年12月 链金术在北京举办《AWDC-DAPP生态发展高峰论坛》
description_en:
In 2018, lianjinshu， a blockchain-based information platform. Our goal is to build China’s first-class blockchain community, to facilitate development and advancement of blockchain industry and technology.
May 2018, Lianjinshu participated the TRON SR election campaign and re-elected ever since.
Meanwhile, Lianjinshu participated EOS Mainnet’s global declaration and assisted the security test.
June 2018, Lianjinshu off-line activities started.
July 2018, Lianjinshu weekly on-line activities started.
August 2018, Original articles from Lianjinshu KOLs made a loud sound widely to guide the DAPP circle. 
September 2018, Lianjinshu audio programs Ten O’clock Blockchain came online.
December 2018, Lianjinshu held the conference AWDC-DAPP Ecological Development Summit Meeting in Beijing.

name: MetaNode
statement:
我们成为IOST在日本的支柱节点。
我们为IOST搭建中日合作的桥梁。
我们是联结节点的节点，我们是MetaNode。
statement_en:
For IOST, we are the strategic support in Japan.
For IOST, we are the bridge between Japan and the world.
We are the node uniting nodes. We are MetaNode.
description: MetaNode是专注于为优质区块链项目做节点治理的社区组织。MetaNode是日本数字财经孵化支持的日本首个专业节点治理组织。MetaNode同时还获得了日本多家专业区块链媒体的支持。
description_en: MetaNode is a community organization focusing on serving as the node for the first-class rising blockchain projects. MetaNode has obtained the incubation support from Digital Journal, and becomes the first professional node organization in Japan. MetaNode has also been supported by several top blockchain media in Japan.

name: 信仰 IOST
statement: 将全力以赴支持IOST生态建设 让更多人支持IOST并积极参与IOST社区建设 与大家一起支持IOST生态经济大发展 并最终成为区块链行业的独角兽。
statement_en: We will get as many people as possible to support IOST and get involved in IOST ecosystem building. Let us work together to push forward IOST’s development and make IOST a unicorn in the blockchain industry.
description: 我和我的伙伴以我个人名义参加IOST的节点。我们将团队合作，全力以赴致力于宣传 推广IOST，令IOST生态经济大发展。
description_en: I will represent my friends to participate in the IOST Partner Program. We will be fully united in our efforts to promote IOST and drive its ecosystem building.

name: Theseus
statement: 引爆IOST区块链的无尽力量
statement_en: Unleash the power of IOST blockchain.
description: Theseus (忒修斯) 是IOST旗下孵化的一家专注于区块链应用的海外研发团队，其目标是在区块链有潜力改造的行业中开发出面向消费者和企业的实际应用，并通过开发在IOST区块链上的DApp启发和帮助更多开发者，使得IOST的区块链技术被更多开发者以及用户所使用。
description_en: Theseus is an IOST-incubated R&D team dedicated to pushing the envelope in blockchain technology and paving the way for the IOST developer community. Its stated goal is to develop practical applications for consumers and companies in industries that can potentially be transformed by utilizing the power of the IOST blockchain. In the process of developing dApps on the IOST blockchain, the Theseus team also aims to inspire and assist more developers, promoting the growth of the IOST blockchain developer community.

name: IOST Seoul
statement: IOSTSeoul은 글로벌 블록체인 컨설팅 회사이며 한국 및 해외 프로젝트들을 엑셀러레이팅 한 귀중한 경험으로 IOST Servi Node를 운영해 나갈 생각이며 또한 Youtube Influencer 와도 같이 마케팅 활동을 할 예정입니다.투명한 BP로써 사용자분들이 신뢰할 수 있는 Servi Node를 구축하는 것이 첫 번째 목표입니다. 저희는 Servi Node를 위해 최소 시스템 요구사항 이상의 컴퓨팅 파워를 제공할 것입니다. 노드 및 사용자들과 즉각적인 의사소통을 하며 의견을 IOST에 전달하고 빠른 피드백을 드릴 수 있는 프로세스를 만들어 나가는 것이 저희의 목표입니다. 어떤 메인넷 프로젝라도 프로젝트와 Dapp 그리고 소비자가 원활하게 의사소통 하는 것은 어렵습니다. IOST, ecosystem Dapp, 그리고 소비자와의 Bridge가 돼서, 그 역할을 저희가 확실하게 해내겠습니다.

IOST, ecosystem Dapp, 그리고 소비자와의 Bridge가 돼서, 그 역할을 저희가 확실하게 해내겠습니다.
description: IOST Seoul은 IOST ecosystem을 믿고 있기 때문에 작년부터 내부적으로 IOST를 많이 수집 중입니다. 최소 물량에 안주하지 않고 더 많은 보트를 얻기 위한 기획을 하고 있습니다. 추후에 공개될 저희 팀원들은 국내 블록체인 커뮤니티에서 많은 활동을 하는 인원들로 구축되어 있습니다. 이러한 팀원들의 경험들을 통해 IOST Ecosystem을 최대한 많은 User들에게 마케팅, 커뮤니티 운영, 밋업, 포럼, 에어 드롭, 등을 할 것이며 좋은 콘텐츠를 Feedback을 통해 확장할 예정입니다.

description_en: Christian, Father, Husband, Blockchain believer, supporter, evangelist, and developer. Business builder, co founder of Monarch Token, philanthropist and future seeker.

name: IOST.BEST NODE
statement: IOST.BEST NODE未来将长期维护IOST网络，与DApps开发者保持合作关系，并与给我们投票的社群保持开放，诚实，紧密的联系。我们的telegram网址https://t.me/bestiost。我们将把30–40% 的收益重新投入到Servi Node的开发中。努力让社群更加了解IOST项目，推广开发者团队的思想。并月度更新IOST BEST NODE的动态进展。感谢IOST社群对我们的支持，让我们共同努力实现共赢！去中心化与每个人利益攸关，让我们一起努力共同创造美好未来！
statement_en: We have big plans for the development of the IOST project in Russia, which we will implement step by step! Make profit with the best, vote for the IOSTBEST node.
description: 我们是来自俄罗斯的数字货币爱好者。我们在2018年早期了解了IOST项目，并萌生了为IOST团队创建一个去中心化世界的创新愿景。我们都是IOST的持有者，但是也需要你们的投票助力我们成为合伙人。如果我们被成功投为合伙人，我们将会自行运行服务器。我们诚邀各位区块链爱好者为我们投票，我们始终坚信世界秩序正在发生深刻调整，技术变革让人们变得更自由，更快乐。让我们携手努力让世界变得更好。
description_en: We are the IOSTBEST NODE team from Russia. We have been working with the IOST project since the launch of the test network - the beginning of February 2019 and ave been actively developing IOST in Russia and Eastern Europe. In the first month of the operation of the main network, we earned the trust of voters - having received the status of a node. For our contribution to the development of the IOST ecosystem, we take honorable places in the ranking of the nodes. Our team was the first in Russia to implement the IOST token into the real sector of economy. Yes, we are proud of it! We share our daily income with our voters and publish this information in our telegram group – you are welcome to visit us. Our team is open to partnerships and offers. We are ready to share our knowledge – feel free to reach out to us.

name: IOST Venture Labs
statement: 我们将积极推动IOST的应用的开发和落地。
statement_en: We will actively support the development and adoption of fun and exciting applications on the network.
description: IOST Venture Labs致力于将最好的DApps带入IOST 生态系统。我们总部设在新加坡，为新加坡项目的产品开发、规模扩展和进入海外市场提供特别支持。
description_en: IOST Venture Labs focus on bringing in the best DApps for the IOST ecosystem. We are based in Singapore and have special assistance programs for Singapore-based projects to develop products, scale up and access overseas markets.

name: SuperONE
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: SuperONE 团队创始人 crazybit 也是 BM 第一个区块链项目 BitShares 的资深参与者，同时也是 BitShares 见证人节点之一的负责人，对石墨烯底层有深入的研究。SuperONE 团队运营了 EOS 备份节点，同时做了一款全球首个社区与钱包一站式综合服务平台 EOS LIVE，在节点运营、钱包开发、内容平台建设、DApp 运营等方面积累了丰富的经验。我们会对 IOST 生态做出如下贡献，包括但不限于钱包开发与推广、内容宣发、DApp 开发与运营等。
statement_en: The SuperONE team founder, crazybit, is a senior participant in BitShares, the first blockchain project at BM, and the head of one of the BitShares Witness nodes, with in-depth research on the underlying graphene. SuperONE team members from Sohu, HSBC, IBM, Sanqi Mutual Entertainment and other well-known Internet companies at home and abroad, have many years in the fields of blockchain, cryptography, smart contracts, security protection and decentralized operation and maintenance. We will make contributions to IOST ecosystem not only in wallet development and promotion, content distribution, DApp development and operation, etc.
description: SuperONE 团队在石墨烯技术领域有长达 5 年的深入研究和运营石墨烯节点的丰富经验，并且也有能力开发服务于社区的产品，我们同时开发了 BitShares 钱包和全球首个社区与钱包一站式综合服务平台 EOS LIVE，可谓深耕石墨烯领域多年的技术流和审美流。SuperONE 团队创始人 crazybit 也是 BM 第一个区块链项目 BitShares 的资深参与者，同时也是 BitShares 见证人节点之一的负责人，对石墨烯底层有深入的研究。SuperONE 团队成员来自搜狐、汇丰、IBM、三七互娱等国内外知名互联网企业，在区块链、密码学、智能合约、安全防护及分布式运维、iOS 和安卓研发等领域均有多年的深耕经验，并有亿级产品开发、运营经验，是一支综合能力强劲、严谨务实的技术团队。
description_en: The SuperONE team has 5 years of in-depth research and operation of graphene nodes in graphene technology, and has the ability to develop products that serve the community. We also developed the BitShares wallet and the world's first community and wallet one stop platform EOS LIVE . We have digged deep on the fronts of technology and aesthetics in the graphene technology. The SuperONE team founder, crazybit, is also a senior participant in BitShares, the first blockchain project at BM, and the head of one of the BitShares Witness nodes, with in-depth research on the underlying graphene. SuperONE team members from Sohu, HSBC, IBM, Sanqi Mutual Entertainment and other well-known Internet companies at home and abroad, have many years in the fields of blockchain, cryptography, smart contracts, security protection and decentralized operation and maintenance, iOS and Android R&D. Some of the team members have development and operation experience in products worth above RMB 100. We are indeed a strong, rigorous and pragmatic team.

name: CRYPTO TIMES
statement: 向日本区块链爱好者传递IOST的正确信息。IOST在日本的社区建设有很大的发展空间。因此，为了让更多的IOST社区在我们的medium平台上建立社交网络，我们将通过技术和宣传活动来支持IOST的发展。
statement_en: Dispatch the correct information of IOST to Japan.Also, at present, the IOST community in Japan is small, few standing up. Therefore, in order to make many IOST communities launch using our "medium":  we will support marketing by technical part and distribution of activities of IOST in Japan.
description: CRYPTO TIMES 是IOST在日本的媒体合作伙伴。CRYPTO TIMES 是日本报道数字货币和区块链新闻的专业媒体，我们的月度流量已经达到41万。CRYPTO TIMES是在日本最早报道IOST的媒体，我们曾经采访了IOST的创始团队。
description_en: CRYPTO TIMES is a local media partner of IOST in Japan.CRYPTO TIMES, which is a specialized media for encryption currency and block chain in Japan, now has a monthly Traffic number of 410,000.For Japan, the correct information of IOST is delivered earlier than anywhere, and original content such as an interview with the Founder team is also being delivered.

name: iost-Q.E.D
statement: 我们提供以下开发工具:1.IOST的Chrome延展（正如以太坊上的Metamask）；2. Web IDE -让开发活动更加容易， ABI调用
statement_en: We will provide following developer tools:1. Chrome extension for IOST. (Kind of Metamask on Ethereum)2. Web IDE - Make developer easy to develop, call ABI.
description: iost-Q.E.D是将在IOST区块链上构建的开发人员社区。要想让IOST成为最好的区块链，制作一个dApp当然是必不可少的。然而，在这之前，好的dApp是由好的开发人员工具(工具包)组成的。我们将为那些甚至没有区块链编程经验的开发人员提供工具。我们的主要客户是开发人员，开发人员将提供好玩的dApp。这是我们的目标。
description_en: iost-Q.E.D is the community of developers who will build on IOST blockchain. For IOST to be the best blockchain to be used, it is essential to make a dApp of course. However, before doing that, good dApp is made from good developer tools(toolkit). We will provide tools for developer who even don't have experience about blockchain programming. Our main customer is developer, and the developer will provide playful dApp. That's our goal.

name: Timechain
statement: Timechain 将彻底改变IOST用户的钱包体验。为了加速IOST应用的落地，超越以DPoS为机制的TRON和EOS,我们将简化用户使用服务的复杂性。我们将帮助更多企业在IOST网络上创新。我们将为每个钱包设置一个包含IOST连接和web服务的价格来帮助企业使用网络。这种SaaS模式将大大提高Dapps构建的质量，帮助企业能够专注于创新，而不是配置和基础设施的搭建。
statement_en: Timechain will revolutionize the wallet experience of IOST users. In order to drive adoption and compete with other DPoS such as TRON and EOS we need to simplify the experience and minimize the complexity of using the services. On the backend, we will building tool and API services for businesses to innovate using the IOST network. Simply by having a price per wallet which will include IOST connections and web services, this will help businesses use the network. This SaaS model will greatly enhance the quality of Dapps build and enable teams to focus on innovation instead of the configuration and infrastructure setup.
description: 每一个区块链项目都肩负着一个使命，我们不仅要通过区块链技术来创新，优化现有的方式，联系和影响用户，我们还要在历史中留下印记。Timechain致力于成为区块链技术和用户的中间桥梁。我们在建设区块链社区的同时，也通过对社区的奖励，数字货币质押和相关的投票活动赢得收益。用户无需有技术背景就可以玩转IOST。Timechain钱包可以帮助用户通过安卓或苹果系统上的应用就可以参与到区块链技术的革命洪流中。
description_en: Every blockchain has a mission to realize—mission that will not only engage, innovate, optimize, improve, and impact their users, but that will also deliver history landmark goals. Timechain aims to be the bridge between blockchain services and consumers.We simplify the experience of being part of a blockchain community and being able to reap the reward such as bounty, staking and voting. Consumers want to be able to use IOST now without coding background. The Timechain wallet enables users to participate and use the latest technology available from one simple mobile application on Android or iOS (Apple).

name: IOSTChensir
statement: 为超越ETH和EOS而共同努力！
statement_en: Let us make concerted efforts to make IOST better than ETH and EOS!
description: 本人浙江人，浙江人的商业嗅觉告诉我，错过了互联网电子商务的机遇，不能再错过这波区块链的机会了。这次的合伙人计划让我们这样的小散也能参与集中，实属万幸，IOST公链需要更多的人参与才能保证社区活跃度，希望我的参加能带动更多的人为IOST做出贡献。
description_en: People from Zhejiang province are famous for their business acumen, with which I myself，as a Zhejinger, are supposed to possess. My advice is do not miss the opportunities the blockchain is bringing us, not repeat your mistakes when e-commerce presented the same to you! I’m proud to participate in the IOST Global Partner Program. We need more people to join us to build IOST community. I would do my best to make IOST better!

name: 公益联盟
statement: 【勇争第一】币达是IOST主网首个领取当选奖励并即时分红且最活跃的节点、是运行稳定高速出块、生态贡献分值最高的节点、是IOST基金会、币市BISS的战略合作伙伴。现拥有6000公众号、weibo粉丝+5个币达股东微信群，线上线下多渠道强力推广宣传，持续为IOST生态引入大量新鲜血液。【五个100%全分红+空投】本节点获得的全部当选奖励、投票奖励100%全分红给投票者、出块奖励100%全分红给dapp开发者及本节点贡献者、使节点每个季度获得更高额贡献奖励和邀请奖励，全部贡献奖励+邀请奖励再100%全分红给投票者邀请者，额外再➕节点孵化的所有项目空投新币奖励➕股东群定期红包和股东特权。完美机制和分红政策确保了联盟良性循环可持续发展，币达信誉度和人才持续增加，发展越来越强大！投票攒币轻松穿越牛熊，囤价值币直达财富自由！
statement_en: IOST Node of Public Interest promises the high returns for the voters.(5 items which promise 100% bonus distribution+airdrop rewards)All the bonuses of us being elected or of voting for us will be 100% distributed to the voters, and block producing rewards will also be 100% given back to the developers, the promoters and contributors. We will give away contribution and referral rewards. Besides, we will airdrop more rewards to our community members. We believe the virtual recycle, credibility and the constant increase of the new talents will make us stand out among all the nodes, which will also bring more rewards to the community. You will become our shareholder if you vote for us. We look forward to you joining us.
description: 本联盟由原大掌柜暴富联盟、币达财富、飞天小猪、清流资本、IOST未来已来、IOSTwealth等众多节点强强联盟，号召区块链信仰群、Dapp开发者、IOST大户、币圈自媒体共同发起，聚币圈有信仰有情义高素质人才携手共发展，充分利用各团队优势及区块链资源，全面建设好IOST社群及繁荣生态。现每天到账的投票收益仅当选奖励的50%，额外还有币达高额专属奖励(另50%+贡献奖励100%+邀请奖励100%)季末私下手动转币https://jinshuju.net/f/BIj9AL 提交收币地址，币年化收益36~80%，远高于火币矿池4重收益和全球任何节点。投【节点联盟】躺赚100%节点收益，大于你自己单做节点(服务器成本+盯守维护+运营)，更省心更专注更强大！诚邀各节点和大户合作，原木桶定律己随时代发展为长板理论，强强联合各挥所长，贡献卓越收益更高，以信为本，以合为贵！
description_en: The alliance was initiated by the blockchain believers, miners,Flying Pig, dapp developers and big EOS holders, we-media professionals in cryptocurrency industry, and the early investors in cryptocurrencies. The alliance was built for the purpose of making more people benefit from blockchain development. We all are big IOST holders and beneficiaries. The operation overheads are minimal for us. We are determined to contribute to IOST community and ecosystem building, promotion through multiple channels, and more. We will do everything possible to make IOST great and prosperous. We will strive for bringing benefits to all members in this alliance.

name: IOST MEdi
statement: IOST MEdi 在DPoS 为基础的区块链已经有丰富的经验，我们正在给一些区块链项目提供去中心化解决方案、目前基于DPoS的解决方案的主要问题之一是将其规模化地用于系统和token. IOST MEdi 将致力于支持DApp的开发者，并助力建立一个健康的生态系统。我们不关注区块生产，而是致力于成为健康生态的搭建者。
statement_en: IOST MEdi has already a strong tradition in DPOS blockchain and already is having projects looking for decentralization solutions. One of the main concerns of current based DPOS solutions are projects that bring mass adoption to system and token. IOST MEdi main concern is to support these DAPP developers and promote a healthy ecosystem; building blocks is not our work, our aim is to become architects of a healthy ecosystem!
description: IOST MEdi是DPoS 为基础的区块链的节点生产者，我们已经在EOS主网上成功创建了项目和社群。为了实现业务多元化，我们此次真诚加入IOST的合伙人竞选计划，努力成为IOST网络的区块生产节点。IOST MEdi将作为一个区块生产技术公司和项目/DApp的孵化器，我们对亚洲，欧洲，非洲等地区充满浓厚兴趣。欢迎你们就如何提高你们的项目提供各种反馈意见。
description_en: IOST MEdi is a branch of large node producer for DPOS blockchain, with several successful projects and community development in EOS mainnet the company diversifies entering in IOST block producing candidate. IOST MEdi acts as a block producer technology company and project / DAPP incubator with strong interest in several regions like Asia, Europe and Africa. Please provide us your feedback and suggestions on how to improve best practices and support your project or interest.

description_en: We are a blockchain development company. We are going to grow Russian community of developers & investors by developing Russian IOST Website & other marketing activities in Russia.

description: Crypto Daily为120,000订阅者定期推出数字货币视频。Crypto Daily是 YouTube上最大，最受欢迎和发展最快的数字货币频道之一。
description_en: Crypto Daily makes regular crypto videos for over 120,000 subscribers. One of the biggest, most respected and fastest growing cryptocurrency channels on YouTubers.

description: IOST BEST是深耕IOST生态的中国节点。致力于推广、发展IOST生态。团队包含多名投资人、区块链知名自媒体、开发者。节点创始人自媒体作者贾慧杰从2017年开始持续输出区块链内容，对区块链行业有着深刻认知，同时也是IOST的支持者。团队将从多维度支持、推广、参与IOST生态。
description_en: IOST BEST is the Chinese node of deeply cultivating IOST ecology. To promote and develop IOST ecology. The team includes several investors, well-known "we media" of blockchain and developers. Jia huijie, founder of node and author of "we media", has been continuously output blockchain content since 2017. He has a deep understanding of the blockchain industry and is also a supporter of IOST. The team will support, promote and participate in IOST ecology from multiple dimensions.

description: 我和我的伙伴以我个人名义参加IOST的节点。我们将团队合作，全力以赴致力于宣传 推广IOST，令IOST生态经济大发展。
description_en: I will represent my friends to participate in the IOST Partner Program. We will be fully united in our efforts to promote IOST and drive its ecosystem building.

name: MXC抹茶交易所

statement_en: We will be the backbone of IOST in the community of digital currency enthusiasts.We firmly believe that IOST will provide a platform for more enterprises and users to achieve value. We are MXC Matcha exchange. Please vote for us!
description: MXC抹茶交易所是由华尔街以及日本欧洲资深量化交易团队联合区块链资深从业者通过去中心化自组织形式创立的一个专注于区块链资产交流和交换的平台。MXC将为用户提供更加安全、便捷、智能的区块链资产流通服务，聚合全球优质区块链资产，融合全球最顶尖的安全技术，致力于打造全球顶级的区块链资产交易平台。
description_en: MXC Matcha exchange is a platform focusing on exchange and exchange of blockchain assets created by Wall Street and senior quantitative trading teams from Japan and Europe in collaboration with senior practitioners of blockchain through decentralized self-organization. MXC will provide users with more secure, convenient and intelligent blockchain asset circulation services, aggregate the world's high-quality blockchain assets, integrate the world's top security technology, and commit to build the world's top blockchain asset trading platform.

name: Blockchain Kyoto

description_en: Blockchain Kyoto is blockchain study group in Kyoto, Japan. In 13 Jan 2019, we hold IOST Workshop with Terry Wang, Meet IOST, and Eversystem. We will hold IOST's developer's workshop every month! And expand IOST economy.

Previously I was an executive for startups having founded or worked at eight companies with four exits and four companies still operating. I am presently highly involved with the blockchain community and active investor

I started to know cryptocurrency when I went to school in America. I was shocked when I saw the end of 2017’s bullish market in cryptocurrency. One time when I pick some cryptocurrency charts to check, I found out IOST, IOST had close to 500% rise in 2 months. IOST is fully decentralized cryptocurrency. I believe cryptocurrency is the future. The way that IOST team is doing, I think it will be the shining star of the future. I will do my best to promote the IOST community. I am looking forward to see IOST will show up in a lot of potential DApps. Let’s make the IOST community stronger and greater. Please vote for me. Thank you.

Berminal is the #1 cryptocurrency news app in English that aggregates stories and news from various major sites like Coindesk, Cointelegraph, CCN, Cryptobriefing, etc. Berminal has more than 1 million users and is an industry leader in the cryptocurrency news apps.

Bermi will be integrated with IOST network after its main net launch in order to create fundamental support and real use case for blockchain technology. Bermi allows our users to have a unified online currency across countries where the underlying technology is powered by IOST and our users’ creation will be fairly measured by cryptocurrency.

Our node will provide a stable service to ensure IOST will thrive and take the blockchain to the next level. Vote for SquareOne-IOST.

Huobi Wallet has supported over 10 currencies like BTC, ETH, EOS, TRX, USDT, and tokens on ERC20, EOS, TRC10 and TRC20.
