statement: 我计划做一名DApp的开发者。同时，我也同样重视社区建设。我将通过社交媒体渠道如"Youtube":   "twitter":  Telegram等宣传IOST.
statement_en: Building a strong Community is our main focus. We intend to do that through social media engagement, bringing investors, developers and offering additional incentive (rewards) to our voters.
description: 大家好，我是一名区块链爱好者，热爱区块链技术为基础的生态系统。我是一名药剂师，但是区块链技术已成为我的新爱好。除了做一名投资者，我想从更深入地融入到生态建设中，而选择IOST这个项目是因为它是一个有潜能的完美项目。我热爱IOST这个明星团队，他们的社区建设和他们独特的PoB共识机制。IOST的技术突破了第三代协议。我个人比较喜欢区块链编程，并希望能够在IOST网络创立DApps.请为我投票，请为IOSToronto投票。
description_en: We are Crypto/Blockchain enthusiasts based in Canada and love this ecosystem. Professionally our background is Science (Chemistry to be precise) but blockchain became our new passion. We wanted to get involved on a different level aside from being investors and felt IOST is that perfect project. IOST is lead by a great Team, their laser focus on Community building, its unique Consensus (POB) and sticking to their core values (Decentrilization/Scalibility/Security).Please vote for the little dreamers! vote IOSToronto!!

name: BlockDevs Asia
statement: 作为亚洲的区块链开发者团队，我们将通过meetup活动和开展相关课程帮助开发者在IOST网络内建立应用，助力IOST在菲律宾/东南亚开发者社区的发展。同时，我们将支持IOST的Bug Bounty Program,为社区建立开发者工具。由于我们致力于在菲律宾/东南亚地区培养和支持技术人才，我们计划于当地的大学合作，给优秀的技术人才提供奖学金，助力他们发挥自己的技术潜能。
statement_en: As BlockDevs Asia we are proactively supporting the Filipino and South-east Asian Developers community. We do this by creating meetups & educational courses, which are designed to help developers getting started to work on top of IOST and build out the Internet of Services.Aside from the educational & meetup part, we also are contributing to the Bug Bounty program. To add, we have developed tooling for starting blockchain developers to help them with developing with this new technology. Our future vision is to make blockchain and thus IOST, accessible to all developers. On the roadmap there are great collaboration with universities for study grants & educational programs.
description: BlockDevs Asia是一个由软件开发者，技术和想要了解区块链DApps和系统开发的商人组成的团队。我们组织的技术交流会注重技术开发，与一群热衷技术的开发者研究区块链，交流会将对所有有兴趣的人开放。与IOST合作后，我们将帮助更多的开发者了解IOST，并一起探索服务互联网的更多可能。
description_en: BlockDevs Asia is a non-profit community group by and for software developers, technology enthusiasts and business people looking to learn more about developing (actual) blockchain apps or systems. By organizing free educational meetups about complex & technical topics, we dive together with a large group of passionate developers into advance blockchain technology. To date we organized more than 20 events, 2 large hackathons and 20 meetups.For the IOST partnership we are focusing on educating our community about the IOST technology and exploring together what the possibilities of the Internet of Services are. BlockDevs Asia contributes by promoting & educating IOST to the community of the Philippines and even across multiple South-east Asian countries.

name: IOST LATINO
statement: 拉丁美洲目前是一个待开发的加密社区仍缺乏的“西部地区”，这不但不是阻碍，反而是IOST未来发展的巨大机遇。近期，巴西和委内瑞拉等国家对区块链技术表现出浓厚的兴趣，但是很多人依然不了解区块链技术可以带来的红利。IOST LATINO将在拉美地区大力宣传IOST, 将其市场扩展到更多国家，我们将向大众展示IOST给我们带来的财务自由，宣传IOST的真正用例。为了成为IOST的合作伙伴，我们将投入更多的努力和热情来促进IOST项目的发展，真正将拉美成为IOST的市场地盘。
statement_en: Latin America is still a territory with scarce cryptographic communities, this instead of being an obstacle is a big opportunity for the growth of IOST, recently countries like Brasil and Venezuela have shown an interest in the Blockchain technology but many citizens ignore the benefits of it."IOST LATINO" wants to announce the goodnesses of IOST to the people in countries where we have presence and then to extend our scope to other countries, we want to show the financial freedom that it offers us; promoting a real use.To be elected partner, we will show great effort and enthusiasm to contribute to the growth of the project and make Latin America an IOST territory.
description: 我们是一个由在市场营销，宣传，网页设计和区块链有广泛知识的成员组成的团队。我们的业务遍及阿根廷、委内瑞拉、哥伦比亚和秘鲁;我们在网站设计、平面设计、宣传和网络钱包配置领域为一些南美加密项目做出了贡献。我们希望在整个拉美地区创建一个大型的支持IOST的社区，并通过宣传IOST的落地应用向社群展示IOST的真正优势。
description_en: We are a team integrated by members with broad knowledge in marketing, publicity, web design, and Blockchain.We have presence in countries as Argentina, Venezuela, Colombia, and Peru; we have contributed with some South America cryptographic projects in web design, graphic design, publicity, and web wallet configuration areas. We want to create a large PRO IOST community in all the Latin region and showing the benefits of it by promoting real and massive use.

We believe that building a complete ecosystem will be a strong advantage as an IOST node candidate and will allow all the investors to thrive in the long run. Vote for us and we will make impossible possible!

description_en: Krypital Group is a leading consulting firm specializing in comprehensive Blockchain marketing and management services to clients worldwide. With operating offices in important metropolises globally, Krypital has helped our clients grow exponentially while setting industry standards over and over again.

name: 牛眼区块链
statement: 我相信IOST的价值，也愿意将IOST节点价值化。投我一票吧！我会用我自己的努力来回报大家，让我们团结一致，共同前进！
statement_en: I believe in the value of IOST, and I’m keen to bring value to IOST nodes. Vote for me, and I will give back to the voters through my consistent contribution. Let us make united efforts and push forward together.
description: 本人王麒乐，大学本科毕业，2015年从传统行业进入比特币挖矿行业，2017年初开始专注区块链一级市场投资，参与了QTUM、GXS、OMG、EOS、AE、SNT、MANA、TRX、CMT、NAS、PAI、IOTX的早期投资。2018年10月在北京注册“北京牛眼区块链技术有限公司”开始布局区块链教育行业，并与“三九投资学院”合作创立贵阳三九学院分站。
description_en: My name is Wang Luqi and I’m a college graduate. I began to get hands on the Bitcoin mining since 2015. Starting from 2017, I started to invest in the primary market of cryptocurrencies, and invested in QTUM、GXS、OMG、EOS、AE、SNT、MANA、TRX、CMT、NAS、PAI、IOTX. I registered my company-Beijing Bull Eye Blockchain co., LTD in Oct. 2018, focusing the blockchain education. Besides, we also built a branch school in GuiYang City in cooperation with Sanjiu Investment Training School.

description: The CryptoStache是针对数字货币行业初学者的教育平台，我们用通俗易懂的方式向学习者介绍以区块链技术为基础的通证，区块链项目和其他相关内容。我们将为初学者和专家提供相关节点建立和其流程的具体介绍，初学者学习课程之后将能够自己建立节点。CryptoStache是迄今为止首个为区块链初学者提供具体学习内容的教育平台。
description_en: The CryptoStache is an education platform for beginners in cryptocurrency that focuses on easy to understand explanations of new blockchain based tokens, projects, and more. All node setup & processes will be documented for beginners & experts alike to learn from and be able to setup their own nodes. No other node operator does this.

statement: 我将通过各种媒体渠道，如YouTube等来宣传IOST。

description: Ben Armstrong，又名比特男孩，是来自亚特兰大地区的加密货币的KOL。2012年，当Ben 第一次购买比特币时，他对加密货币产生了兴趣。2018年，他创建了自己专用的加密货币通道BitBoy Crypto。除了制作新闻和教育视频，Ben还专注于加密较轻松的一面，包括创建迷因、视频和模仿秀等。
description_en: Ben Armstrong, aka BitBoy, is a crypto influencer from the Atlanta area. Ben first became interested in cryptocurrency in 2012 when he made his first Bitcoin purchase. In 2018, he started his own dedicated cryptocurrency channel called BitBoy Crypto. Along with making news & educational videos, Ben also focuses on the lighter side of crypto including creating memes, videos, & parodies.

description_en: Protocol researcher & Developer. Calculating BFT rate and analyzing attacks. Also developing Dapps on many protocols.

name: Crypto Brekkie
statement: 我会利用在数字货币&区块链行业和在内容制作的已有经验宣传IOST，让更多的人了解和支持IOST的生态发展。
statement_en: I will use my experience in the crypto & blockchain space as well as my track record of creating viral content to promote awareness and support the growing IOST ecosystem.
description: 我是内容创作者、艺术家、设计者，更是去中心化、低门槛区块链技术、隐私保护和金融自主的狂热支持者。我相信数字货币的美好未来！
description_en: Content creator, artist, designer, and avid supporter of decentralization, permission-less blockchain tech, privacy, and financial sovereignty. I believe in a CRYPTO future.

name: Magnum Wallet
statement: 作为一个创建轻量级非托管钱包的团队，我们可以为IOST用户提供许多有价值的选择。在主网推出后，我们开始支持IOST coin，并将在未来为用户提供内置交易所、记账支持、投票、DApp市场、交易跟踪等额外功能。作为一项叠加服务，我们将努力吸引新用户加入IOST社区，我们也会通过可靠的渠道来推广IOST。
statement_en: As a team that is creating a light non-custodial wallet, we have many valuable options to bring to the IOST users. We started supporting the IOST coin immediately after the launch of the mainnet and will provide our users with extra features such as an in-built exchange, ledger support, voting, DApp Marketplace, transactions tracker bot, etc. in the future. As a stacking service, we are interested in attracting new users to the IOST community, and we have reliable channels to promote promising features of the IOST network.
description: Magnum是一个提供通用的非托管钱包和栈服务的团队。Magnum团队维护节点服务和其他质押功能，为帮助用户赚取被动收入。用户可以通过在Magnum钱包质押数字资产而获取收益。同时，他们也能通过比特币和以太坊分叉获得收入。查看我们的medium文章https://medium.com/@corp_92607了解具体操作指南。我们的使命是帮助用户增加财富和保护用户的财产安全。我们的用户对私钥拥有完全的控制权，私钥储存在加密的备份文件里。同时，Magnum支持硬钱包，为用户提供最安全的操作数字货币的方式。
description_en: Magnum is a universal non-custodial wallet and stacking service. The Magnum team maintains a node service and other staking features to provide users with passive income. They can earn by staking and delegating their coins in Magnum Wallet. Also, they can get extra coins by claiming 20+ Bitcoin and Ethereum forks. You can find guides on how to use these features on https://medium.com/@corp_92607 Our mission is to increase the wealth of our users and to help them keep their coins safe. That’s why users have sole control over the private keys which are stored in their encrypted backup files. Also, Magnum supports hardware wallets to provide users with the safest way to operate cryptocurrency.

name: IOST.space

statement_en: With the continuation of events, members of this community will increase. Activities not only in urban areas but also in rural areas will be made public in Japan. Hospitality technology market is a huge.

I would like to make it a community that contributes to shortage of talented people and successor problems of rural hotels and inns. Voters are all people who are related to hospitality industry.

description: IMS Medica是一家从事创建医疗应用的公司。
description_en: IMS Medica is a company specializing in creating applications for health care.

name: IOSTcallister
statement: 我的目标是让尽可能多的人参与到IOST社区中来，告诉其他人投资是多么重要，不仅仅是投资于加密货币，而是投资于我们的未来。IOST将释放区块链的力量，请为IOSTcallister投票。

description_en: IOSTcallister is promoting through social media to educate our communities on the life changing opportunities that IOST has to offer. I would like to instruct and influence as many people and our future generations how important the blockchain technology is to our ecosystem.

name: BEPAL
statement: BEPAL分别作为BTM、EOS、GXC生态节点，我们在维护节点生态上有着更多优势。齐全的产品线及服务项目为我们带来更多优质用户。我们十分认同POB共识机制，将致力于支持和发展IOST生态，用丰富的用户群体、卓越的技术支持、领先的市场占有率、知名的品牌影响力为IOST生态服务。助力IOST主网上线，共同维护IOST生态！请为BEPAL投出宝贵的一票！
statement_en: BEPAL is already a BP for BTM，EOS and GXC due to our BP advantages. BEPAL attracts numbers of customers with good products and services. We agree to consensus mechanism. We are going to support and develop IOST ecosystem with our outstanding technology and well-known brand. Support IOST mainnet and ecosystem.Please vote for us.
description: BEPAL是一家技术驱动型的区块链公司，以区块链私钥安全管理技术为核心，提供全场景区块链资产管理产品、资产管理服务平台及行业应用解决方案。现已成功推出BEPAL Pro、BEPAL Q、BEPAL Touch系列安全硬件，BEPAL Wallet数字资产钱包、BEPAL Plus数字资产托管服务，帮助用户安全管理超十亿数字资产。其中，BEPAL PRO S硬件钱包斩获“中国最佳硬件钱包”、“区块链最受关注安全 硬件”等多个奖项。未来，BEPAL将继续致力于推动数字资产管理服务生态。
description_en: BEPAL is a technology-driven Blockchain company. The core of BEPAL is Blockchain private key security management technology. BEPAL provides Blockchain asset management products, platform and industry application solutions. BEPAL has officially launched BEPAL PRO, BEPAL Q, BEPAL Touch etc. Hardware wallets, BEPAL Plus digital asset custody platform. BEPAL helped users to manage their over billion digital assets securely. BEPAL PRO S has won The Best Hardware Wallet in China; The Most Popular Hardware Wallet etc.BEPAL committed to promoting the digital asset management ecology.

name: IOST Pinoy Crypto Enthusiasts
statement_en: We will strive to promote IOST and its Node Partners across a variety of platforms - social media, blog posts and articles to bring in more users into the ecosystem and attract more investors. We will also help raise awareness by providing guidance and education to users and crypto newbies through meetups, awareness sessions, etc. Whatever we earn, we will give back a portion of our election and contribution rewards back to the community in the form of outreach programs to selected communities in the Philippines. Vote for us! Let's bring blockchain to the masses together.
description_en: We are a community of blockchain and crypto enthusiasts, strong advocates and evangelists of the IOST project. We have closely followed IOST since its inception in January 2018 after learning about its groundbreaking innovations of building a better public blockchain. We will promote IOST as a blockchain project of choice for users and investors, it being a fair and truly decentralized network that generously incentivizes nodes and token holders alike.

name: MATPool
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: MATPool将为IOST的节点运行提供安全、稳定的环境，努力为IOST创造更大价值，共建IOST生态，推动IOST更好发展。
statement_en: MATPool will provide a safe and stable environment for IOST node operation, strive to create greater value for IOST, build IOST ecology, and promote IOST better development.
description: MATPool为巴比特旗下矿池平台，MatPool的使命是“融计算，融共识，融价值”，努力建立“标杆性的区块链计算和超级节点服务平台”，服务各类主链共识机制的参与者，为其提供一个稳定、安全、开放的平台环境。

statement: 我将通过视频频道宣传推广IOST，让更多的人了解IOST。我的视频频道将研究可以真正在IOST生态中应用的解决方法。我们将讨论IOST如何利用其技术优势解决真实存在的问题。我的视频频道会报道IOST的最新动态。如果你想看到IOST的视频、新闻和采访，请为我投票。IOST目前在澳大利亚的报道还比较少，请为我投票，让我打破这种趋势。

We'll discuss and debate problems in the real world and find a way IOST can help to alleviate. The channel will keep you informed on what is happening.Vote for me if you want to see IOST:-News -How to Videos -Interviews -Spreading the good word of IOST. IOST has very little Australian coverage, lets break that trend.
description: 我是一个自由主义者。 我认为只要你不伤害别人，你可以做任何你喜欢做的事。我认为社会权力应该更加去中心化，因为人们会做出更好的决定。同时，我是YouTuber，对政治、经济、哲学和策略游戏感兴趣。我喜欢讨论任何事情，但是我不喜欢运动。我看到现在世界正处于金融混乱之中，虽然我们支出了很多，但是却无法避免很多灾难。作为一名乐观主义者，由于数字货币可以通过资本市场，个人财务或社会管理等方面执行去中心化合约，所以我认为数字货币可以帮助我们规避很多灾难。我相信，区块链技术将会颠覆整个社会的生产和生活。
description_en: I’m a libertarian; you can do what you like as long just don’t harm others. I believe we don’t need much government & if more power was left in people’s hands, they’d make better decisions. I am youtuber interested in politics, economics, philosophy and strategy gaming. A guy who’d happily chat about anything as long as it’s not sport (too distracting). I see the world is in financial chaos with so much spending brought forward with little ability to avoid the inevitable collapse. As an optimist, I see cryptos as a way to circumvent the disaster with decentralised contracts in capital markets, personal finance & society. Its about time we have a revolution!

description_en: MANGO is a professional DAPP development team and we are committed to being a benchmark in the global blockchain gaming industry. Through effective integration with the blockchain industry, it can effectively avoid the high cost, slow storage/redemption and lack of trust mechanism of traditional games. Help blockchain trusters, supporters, and gamers gain high dividends by participating in the game while they are having fun. The Mango team has many years of experience in the game industry. They understand the domestic game market, operations and product status. The founders' team members have a history of game companies such as KONAMI, UBISOFT, EPIC-GAMES and some of China's best game companies. At the same time, the Mango team has many years of experience in blockchain investment, and will be the most direct and effective combination of domestic and international game market and blockchain technology, and is committed to creating high-quality game content and innovative gameplay combined with chain and chain. Strive to create a multi-win ecosystem between the community, players, partners and teams.

description: 广州光汇软件科技有限公司（简称“光汇软件”）成立于2004年，是一家集数据、软件、服务于一体的中国领先的地理信息产业服务商。十多年来，光汇软件坚持以空间智能技术为核心，结合云计算、大数据、物联网等先进技术，围绕国土、基础测绘、房产、工商、税务等领域发展地理信息产业，提供数字国土、不动产登记、经济大数据、信息化测绘、"地控税"、云估价等数字城市建设中的软件产品、系统和服务，现涉足区块链领域，是一名新兵。
description_en: Guangzhou Guanghui Software Technology Co., Ltd. (abbreviated as "Guanghui Software") was established in 2004. it is a leading geographic information industry service provider in China, which integrates data, software and service. Over the past decade or so, Guanghui Software has adhered to spatial intelligence technology as the core, combined with advanced technologies such as cloud computing, big data, and the Internet of things, and developed the geographic information industry around the fields of land, basic surveying and mapping, real estate, industry and commerce, and taxation. To provide digital land, real estate registration, economic big data, information mapping, "land control tax", cloud valuation and other digital city construction software products, systems and services, is now involved in the blockchain field.

statement_en: FINDEX as an exchange will use our unique strength on technology development and services, assists in building an excellent ecosystem on IOST, and enables IOST community and participants in achieving a new era of blockchain.
description: FINDEX去中心化交易所，目前已经部署服务于EOS与BOS。团队拥有丰富的区块链底层和智能合约开发经验，基于EOS Plugin技术开发出的分布式撮合引擎，使用智能合约管理所有的订单簿和成交，所有用户行为均被记录在链上。基于撮合引擎的交易机制保证用户体验与传统中心化交易所一致的前提下，完成去中心化的部署。拥有链上智能合约直接撮合、无KYC等特点。目前拥有网页桌面版www.findex.pro、集成钱包的交易渠道和项目方集成渠道。2019年3月，正式加入IOST生态，参与节点合伙人选举，为IOST社区与生态做出自己的贡献。FINDEX也致力于推动多链生态为自己的长远目标。
description_en: FINDEX is a decentralized exchange starting from EOS. The distributed match engine based on EOS Plugin technology utilizes smart contracts to manage all order books and transactions, and all user behavior is recorded on the chain. The decentralized deployment is completed on the premise that the transaction mechanism of the matching engine ensures that the user experience is consistent with the traditional centralized transaction. no KYC is required. Currently users could access FINDEX through desktop version at www.findex.pro, integrated wallet channels and project dApp integrated channels on EOS and BOS. From March 2019, FINDEX joins IOST ecosystem with IOST nodes election as a start. FINDEX also has a vision to develop multi-chain ecosystem in future.

name: IOST Rainbow
statement: 区块链项目面临的最大挑战是如何让开发人员了解在应用程序中使用区块链的潜在好处和特点，以及为他们提供足够简单的材料来学习如何在加密协议之上进行开发。 业界需要更多地了解加密协议以及在区块链上可以构建的app的明确示例。 IOST Rainbow计划通过创建教育材料以及使用全球影响力网络来帮助开发者使用协议并在其上开发应用程序。
statement_en: The biggest challenge to blockchain projects is to educate developers on the potential benefits and characteristics of using blockchain in applications, as well as providing easy enough materials to learn how to build on top of crypto protocols. The industry needs more awareness of crypto protocols and some clear examples of what can be built on blockchain. IOST Rainbow plans to evangelize the platform by creating educational materials as well as using a global network of influencers to help developers adopt the protocol and build applications on it.
description: IOST Rainbow是一个由一群来自世界各地的区块链思想先驱、创业者以及投资者建立的节点。我们的节点致力于通过创建教育资料、宣传以及影响力网络来帮助实现协议的采纳。节点负责人Andrew Lee是一个颇受关注的加密及区块链投资出版物-W3J的创始人，他同时也是几家区块链平台的咨询师，包括QuarkChain、 Chromapolis by ChromaWay、Metadium等等。 我们团队的独特之处在于我们相信社区建设和开源的加密风格。
description_en: IOST Rainbow is a node founded by a group of blockchain thought leaders, entrepreneurs and investors based globally. The node is focused on helping drive real adoption of protocols through creation of educational materials, evangelists and an influential global network. The node is led by Andrew Lee, founder of W3J, a popular crypto and blockchain investing publication. Andrew is also an advisor to several blockchain platforms, including QuarkChain, Chromapolis by ChromaWay, Metadium and more. What makes our group unique is that we believe in the crypto-inspired ethos of community building and open-sourcing. Our goal, since entering the industry, is to add value to contribute to the greater good of the crypto industry. The group is based globally in Americas, Europe and Asia.

name: IOST Watch
statement_en: Our plan is to continue to deliver news, education, and developer tools relevant to the IOST ecosystem. Targeting both developers and end users, our first tool was a Windows 64bit iWallet CLI and our news channel, IOST Weekly Digest reports the highlights of the IOST ecosystem, plus other notable events such as Jimmy Zhong's AMA's on "telegram":  new IOST Partners, and dApps. By leveraging advanced social media analytics we can deliver timely and relevant content ensuring the maximum impact on momentum and adoption of IOST. The focus on developer tools is to help remove friction out of the development process and help propel IOST to be the application development platform for Web 3.0. The next tool to be released is a "one click" script to install and build the entire IOST development environment eliminating the often frustrating process of fighting with dependencies, toolchain setup, and other idiosyncrasies. We are excited and thankful to be part of what is going to be a shift in global computing.
description_en: Jim O'Quinn and Oladayo Oladipupo teamed up to start IOST Watch. We are committed to delivering news, education, and developer tools relevant to the IOST ecosystem. Targeting both developers and end users, our first tool was a Windows 64bit iWallet CLI and our news channel, IOST Weekly Digest reports the highlights of the IOST ecosystem, plus other notable events such as Jimmy Zhong's AMA's on "telegram":  new IOST Partners, and dApps.

name: BlockArcade
statement_en:
We know UX, Go and JavaScript!

With our experience delivering products as a team, we believe we’re uniquely suited to run this node and contribute to IOST. Currently our focus is in 3 main categories: 

1) dApps - We hope to build dApps that give IOST a good name, starting with [blockarca.de](http://blockarca.de/). BlockArcade will use every aspect of the IOST blockchain and will be an example of what's possible. 

2) Design - We've been hard at work on a line of t-shirts that we believe the crypto space just hasn't seen. I know because we've been looking. We believe this is an important contribution because you want to win over developers, and good swag can help get the conversation started. 

3) Apps - When we joined the IOST community we saw an opportunity to use our past experience building desktop applications to build an IOST desktop app. We need your help though! Please stop by our Telegram(@blockarcade) and let us know what you'd like in a desktop app. 

That seems like a lot, and it is. We're excited to help build this community together. We need all the help we can get!
description_en: BlockArcade is a team of entrepreneurs with experience building and delivering end-user applications. In the past we've used Node.js, React/Redux, Electron, Go, C/C++, WebAssembly, and WordPress to build apps. After building on Ethereum we're looking for something that will enable us to build real (user-friendly) applications today, and we believe that is IOST! Looking forward to working with you all.

description: 作为IOST公链上第一个区块链游戏公会，清风链游公会的使命就是：甄选好的游戏，然后在区块链游戏中，带领每一个在现实中因为阶层固化和财富剥削导致才华无法施展，劳动得不到应有回报，但又不甘于现实的朋友们，我们一起，在全新的世界中，去赢得我们该有的一切！我们不但要有钱，还要有自由和快乐，就是这么傲娇！欢迎每一个跟我们有相同人生观、价值观和世界观的朋友加入我们，一起玩出财富和自由！

name: InfStones
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工

name: cryptowar
statement: IOST数字战争致力于IOST生态，从而帮助IOST拓展区块链游戏领域，带来越来越多的Dapps开发者和玩家到IOST上来。
statement_en: We will do our utmost efforts to carry on the mission of building up IOST ecosystem. We will help the IOST to explore the blockchain games fields, and bring more players join in IOST.
description: 是一款SLG游戏的DApp。在游戏中，玩家们扮演中世纪的领主，在大陆上发展生产，缔结联盟，并且为了王座与领土而使用各种手段进行对抗。
description_en: IOST CRYPTOWAR is a SLG game on blockchain. Players could play a landlord of the meddle age in game, and developing product on the mainland. Players also could build own team and fight with other teams for plundering resource.

name: 希格斯网络
statement: Higss Network希格斯网络致力于IOST生态，从而帮助IOST拓展区块链游戏领域，带来越来越多的Dapps开发者和玩家到IOST上来。
statement_en: We will do our utmost efforts to carry on the mission of building up IOST ecosystem. We will help the IOST to explore the blockchain games fields, and bring more players join in IOST.
description: 希格斯网络将是为去中心化应用(DAPPs)所搭建的新一代基础设施网络，将从代币交换的流动性，用户流量导入以及区块链技术服务等三个维度给予去中心化应用(DAPPs) 支持。
description_en: Higgs Network is a infrastructure network which builds for the DAPPS. Higgs Network brings new users liquidity, traffic and blockchain technology development and also provide healthy blockchain game economy system model.

name: Crypto Evangelist
statement_en: I would contribute to IOST project through investing on IOST and creating analytic content about IOST content to make people better understand IOST.
description_en: I was a software developer and now blockchain enthusiast in China. It was during a meetup where I got to know IOST project. I write analytic articles about blockchain technology and discussing blockchain projects.

name: WhaleToBe
statement_en: As we believe in IOST blockchain utility, and the community spirit, we decide to be a part from the beginning, being a window for the blockchain world via IOST democracy.
description_en: WhaleToBe Club is a news magazine wich is going to be an incentive rewarding platform. The site shares high quality transparent articles, and as we was supporting TRON, we are going to support IOST.

name: Institute of Blockchain®
statement: 用教育传播区块链知识
statement_en: Through education to spread blockchain technology.
description: Blockchain Ltd研究所（UEN：201901394N）成立于2018年1月，总部设在新加坡。我们是一家非营利性区块链学校，主要致力于推进和提供区块链教育，认证和区块链研究。截至目前，IBS已在新加坡，香港和迪拜培训了1000多名参与者。该研究所是新加坡技能未来、NTUC e2i和人民协会批准的培训机构，是新加坡政府注册的Gebiz供应商，毕业于阿里巴巴云-SUSS企业家计划。 IBS是ACE初创公司联盟、世界区块链协会和NEM 基金生态的成员。作为我们企业社会责任工作的一部分，我们加入了全国志愿服务与慈善中心的慈善公司项目，并将新加坡儿童协会作为我们的官方慈善机构。我们的战略合作伙伴包括SUSS，Edufied，IBM 校园人才培训计划，DIFY，Justicius 律所和CryptoProfile。我们过去的企业客户包括Deloitte Touche，GCOX，Sainmaco，Ninecoin（香港），团贷（广州），新加坡海关和新加坡理工学院。关于我们：被Crunchbase评选为全球1500强学校。 - 新加坡第一个区块链学校。 - 新加坡第一所接受加密货币作为支付方式的学校
description_en: Institute of Blockchain® Ltd(UEN: 201901394N) was founded on Jan 2018 and based in Singapore. We are a non-profit blockchain school with the primary focus on advancement & delivering blockchain education, certification and blockchain research. Til date, IBS has trained more than 1000 participants in Singapore, Hong Kong & Dubai. The Institute is a SkillsFuture Singapore’s, NTUC e2i’s and People’s Association approved Training Organisation, a registered Singapore Government’s Gebiz supplier and graduated from the Alibaba Cloud-SUSS Entrepreneurship Programme. IBS is a member of ACE Startups, World Blockchain Association and NEM Foundation Ecosystem. As part of our CSR efforts, we joined the NVPC’s Company of Good and adopted Singapore Children’s Society as our official charity. Our strategic partners are SUSS, Edufied, IBM Academic Initiative, DIFY, Justicius Law Corporation & CryptoProfile. Our past corporate clients includes Deloitte Touche, GCOX, Sainmaco, Ninecoin (Hongkong), Tuandai (Guangzhou), Singapore Customs & Singapore Polytechnic. Interesting Facts: – Crunchbase’s Top 1500 schools in the world. – 1st blockchain school in Singapore. – 1st Singapore’s school to accept cryptocurrency as a mode of payment

name: Xangle.io
statement_en: IOST의 메인넷을 On-chain정보를 Indexing하여, on/off chain정보 공시를 통하여 IOST커뮤니티와 potential holder를 위한 충분한 가치를 창출해 내겠습니다.
description_en: 쟁글은 글로벌 암호화폐 시장을 위한 정보공시 플랫폼입니다. 지금까지 크립토 투자자들이 텔레그램이나 미디엄 등의 멀티채널을 검색하여 정보를 찾기 위해 많은 시간을 투자했던 방법을 탈피하고 쟁글을 통해 신뢰성 있는 정보를 보다 편리하게 취득하고 의사결정을 빠르게 내릴 수 있도록 돕고 있습니다. 쟁글의 공시 기준은 DART, EDGAR와 같은 증권 규제 기관의 공시 기준과 국제신용평가사의 평가 기준에 준거하여 재해석되었으며, 토큰 정보뿐만 아니라 사업현황이나 재무상황, 영업실적 등의 종합적인 정보를 포함하고 있습니다.

name: ZeLoJapan
statement_en: ZeLo law firm is formed by lawyers who are specialised on corporate legal affairs and blockchain technology, promptly provides our clients with the highest quality legal services, and always stays close to our clients as their consultant they can fully rely on.
description_en: ZeLo, as a legal expert node, cooperates to maintain the healthy governance in the ecosystem, has a clear understanding of services and regulations which arise as technologies grow, and fosters product developments in IOST network by utilising blockchain technology.

name: 峰果矿池
statement: IOST，区块链的未来。区块链，世界的未来。
description: 峰果矿池来自一家拥有多年开发经验的互联网公司。通过对区块链深入的研究与探索，团队正不断致力于将区块链带到每个人身边，让越来越多的感受到区块链如同最初的互联网一般，正在逐渐的改变着这个世界。

name: OKEx矿池
statement: OKEx 矿池将以真诚的态度、优质的服务投入到IOST的生态建设中，与IOST社区一起推动IOST生态健康高效发展。
statement_en: OKEx Pool will engage in the ecosystem development of IOST with a sincere attitude and high-quality service, and promote the healthy and efficient development of IOST ecosystem together with the IOST community.
description: OKEx 矿池是一家提供更高收益的创新型矿池，不仅支持BTC、LTC等多种POW挖矿币种，也支持EOS、IOST等多种锁仓挖矿币种。依托于世界领先的数字资产交易平台OKEx，为用户提供安全稳定、公开透明的多币种多类型挖矿服务。
description_en: OKEx Pool is an innovative mining pool that provides miners with higher yields. It currently supports the mining of a plethora of PoW assets, such as BTC and LTC, as well as lock-mining assets, including EOS and IOST. Relying on the world's leading digital asset trading platform OKEx, it provides users with safe, stable and transparent multi-currency multi-type mining services.

name: 节点矿池
type: 其他网络的区块生产者/矿工
statement: 以专业的运维团队保障IOST节点的稳定运行，以雄厚的资金实力助力IOST生态的快速形成，以节点矿池的影响力让更多的人了解IOST，并积极参与到IOST社区建设。与其他优秀的节点一道助力IOST全生态的发展。
statement_en: IM POOL strives to ensure the stable operation of IOST nodes with professional operation and maintenance team, to assist the rapid formation of IOST ecology with strong financial strength, to let more people know about IOST by the influence of IM POOL, and actively participate in the construction of IOST community. Together with other nodes, promotes the development of the whole IOST ecosystem become the next great main-chain.
description: 节点矿池是文储网络和世纪互联共同孵化的国内首个零门槛、多币种、多节点的矿池管理平台。节点矿池还并购瑞典VIINAB公司，对IOST国际化和欧洲社区建设提供帮助。节点矿池依托文储网络的资金及世纪互联的网络支持，拥有强大的硬件研发团队和系统开发团队，也是IPFS开发者大会邀请的首个中国技术团队。节点矿池拥有丰富的矿场和矿池运维经验，并拥有PoW、PoC、PoS和DPoS等多种共识机制的运营经验。
description_en: IM POOL is the first zero-threshold, multi-cryptocurrencies and multi-superIM POOL management platform in China, which is incubated by Filestorer blockchain Tech.&Science co., Ltd. and 21Vianet Broad Band Data Center Co., Ltd. IM POOL also acquired Swedish VIINAB Company, which enable us to help IOST internationalization and to build community in European counties. Depending on the fund of Filestorer blockchain Tech.&Science co., Ltd. and the IDC services and network supports of 21Vianet Broad Band Data Center Co., Ltd., the IM POOL has a strong hardware R&D team and software system development team. It is also the first Chinese technical team invited by the IPFS Developers Conference. IM POOL has rich experience in operation and maintenance of mine and mining pool, and has operational experiences of PoW, PoC, PoS, DPoS and other consensus mechanisms.

name: IFWallet
statement: 连接你与区块链的无限可能。
statement_en: Bring you to the infinite possibilities future of Blockchain.
description: IFWallet 作为一款多链一站式的数字资产存储管理平台，具备区块链领域的深厚积累，年轻有激情的团队基于新的公链，为用户提供安全稳定、简单易用却又丰富多彩的应用。IOST的POB等改进理念，让我们看到大规模应用的可能，IFWallet 希望能成为 IOST 生态的参与者和贡献者，与广大社区成员共建 IOST 的未来。
description_en: IFWallet is a multi-chain Wallet，which is stable, easy to use and colorful. We are looking forward to build more Applications base on powerful blockchain such as IOST. IOST is a better blockchain than EOS and ETH, and more and more people support it. IFWallet hope to become one of you and make great things happen.

name: Coin Club
statement: Coin Club拥有超过百万的区块链用户流量，将通过快讯宣发、广告位推荐、活动宣发、社群互动等多种方式，宣传推广IOST，为IOST生态注入用户流量资源。同时，Coin Club将为IOST链上DApp提供快速推广通道，助力优秀的IOST开发者共享海量用户资源。
statement_en: With more than one million blockchain user community, Coin Club will promote IOST through newsletter announcements, banner recommendations, activity recommendations, and community interactions，which can inject millions of user to join the IOST ecosystem. At the same time, Coin Club will provide a fast promotion channel for IOST DApps, helping excellent IOST developers to share massive user resources.
description: Coin Club是一个面向全球加密货币投资者的开放社区，您可以在其中探索最新鲜的区块链热点和来自顶级新闻网站的最热门新闻，并阅读应用程序中的完整文章。 我们的目标是帮助投资者彼此之间以及与区块链行业的创业公司更有效地沟通和协作，吸引更多的生态建筑合作伙伴和项目，并共同创造一种赋予行业价值的新生态。
description_en: Coin Club is an open community for global cryptocurrency investors, where you can explore freshest selected blockchain hot spots and hottest news within the Coin Club app. Coin Club aims to help investors communicate and collaborate more efficiently with each other and with startups in blockchain industry, attract more ecological construction partners and projects, and jointly create a new ecology that endows the industry with the value of blockchain.

name: 小葱APP
statement: 小葱APP助力IOST生态建设，发现IOST的价值。
statement_en: Xcong APP helps to build the IOST ecology and explore the value of IOST.
description: 小葱是中国顶级财经媒体华尔街见闻旗下，专注区块链和加密货币的金融信息服务商。正在为全球投资者及区块链从业人士提供数字货币和区块链领域领先的资讯、行情、数据服务和研究报告。
description_en: Xcong Network Ltd.- An emerging financial information services provider, portfolio manager and trading terminal that specializes in crypto assets.Company Purpose:We are devoted to providing users with best possible trading services at all times, along with professional, objective and neutral news and reports. Specifically, we have provided users with the latest information on cryptocurrencies and blockchain technology at an unbeatable speed, including analyses of market changes and crypto trading strategies. With a safe and efficient system, our platform has already supported more than 30 exchanges and thousands of coins real-time tickers, helping you keep a track of your crypto portfolio all the time.

name: IOSTFISH
statement: IOSTfish，No.1的区块链休闲养成游戏，边养鱼边赚钱
statement_en: NO.1 blockchain leisure & simulation game in which you can profit at the same time having fun
description: IOSTfish源自NO.1区块链休闲和模拟游戏Fishchain，也是其混合通证系统的一部分。Fishchain是世界上第一个打通金融和消费端的游戏，同时也是基于IOST生态系统的游戏平台和交易所。在金融端，投资者可以购买包含鱼缸和鱼类的挖矿套餐来赚取IOST和IOFISH（一种iosttoken），而在游戏端，玩家会消耗IOST和IOFISH并使用技巧获得乐趣并赢取奖品。
description_en: IOSTfish is derived from the NO.1 blockchain leisure & simulation game Fishchain and part of its hybrid-token system.Fishchain is the first ever game in the world which gets through both investment and consumption ends, and at the same time a game platform and exchange based on IOST ecosystem.At the financial end, investors can buy mining packages which contain fishbowls and fish to mine IOST and IOFISH (an iosttoken), while at the game end, players consume IOST and IOFISH and use tricks to have fun and win prizes.

name: BigFour币福
statement: BigFour币福——让区块链更简单
statement_en: BigFour Wallet - Make Blockchain Easier
description: BigFour币福钱包是一个智能的区块链生活服务平台，除提供安全便捷的支付、转账、收款功能外，更是一个集安全、交易、严选、资管、理财、游戏、文化、社交等多样化场景为一体的开放性服务平台，目前已接入Ethereum、EOS两大生态系统，一步触达上千种分布式应用，区块链从此更简单！BigFour是一个智能的区块链生活服务平台，提供多样的场景化服务，一步触达上千种应用，区块链从此更简单！
description_en: Safe and convenient —Supports multi-chain assets and off-line private key.Dual-chain trading—Supports nearly 100 trading pairs of EOS and ETH for one-stop trading. Cross-chain Support—Reaches thousands of decentralized applications and supports ETH and EOS ecosystems.

name: HashFin
statement: HashFin将整合自身的媒体、交易所、钱包资源，助力搭建IOST底层网络，促进IOST生态的长期发展。

name: 大力士
description: Dex.top团队分布在瑞士、美国、新加坡、香港，核心成员有来自Google、Uber的系统架构专家和项目负责人，也有来自中科大的计算机博士和智能合约专家，以及来自新加坡国立大学、剑桥大学的高级金融人才，团队在区块链底层技术、共识算法、智能合约模型、去中心化数字资产管理、交易结构设计等方面有丰富的经验积累。
description_en: Dex.top is a decentralized Ethereum-token exchange based on the smart contract. It introduces the innovative ROC (Replayed On Chain) trading mechanism that leverages the synchronized off-chain and on-chain ledgers to enable instant trading while making traders' assets safe. Dex.top is committed to providing the most secure, instant, and low-cost trading experience to end users in all levels.

name: 币快报
description: Bitwires致力于打造全球最大的区块链社交媒体平台。为全球区块链从业者提供信息— Bitwires包括中文品牌币快报，以及全球品牌Bitwires, 在2020预期覆盖中文，英文，西班牙文，韩语，日语，阿拉伯语等多语种；合规践行者—创立于新加坡，安全 可信 合规的全球化媒体平台；技术驱动—遍布全球的爬虫体系，内容聚合，个性化推荐；Token 激励—Token经济的践行者，阅读 分享 邀请，都有token激励；基于Token经济，全球增速第一的媒体平台；我们的成绩—Bitwires 旗下币快报是中文区块链第一流量媒体平台，内容覆盖用户近700万人，入驻1000家项目方，800家自媒体，日均资讯快讯量全网第一；在硅谷，东京，新加坡，上海均设有采编团队，7*24小时运转。通证BKBT将是Bitwires品牌旗下所有App的唯一生态通证。
description_en: Bitwires is currently the China's largest blockchain media platform in terms of user traffic! With over 1000 projects and 700 media partners signed on to our platform, Bitwires has reached 2 Million downloads ，its API cooperates with 50 high-traffic apps, covering over 7 Million users.Bitwires is a global blockchain media platform and community, and one of the fastest growing media platforms in the Asia Pacific region.

name: TI Staking
statement: TI-Staking愿与优秀的PoS项目一起共同推进区块链技术和应用的落地。
statement_en: TI-Staking is willing to work together with the excellent PoS project to promote the landing of blockchain technology and applications.
description: TI-Staking是TokenInsight旗下的的Staking业务子品牌，负责参与到PoS项目的生态建设中，为PoS项目提供优势的研究和数据服务
description_en: TI-Staking is a sub-brand of Staking business under TokenInsight. It is responsible for participating in the ecosystem construction of PoS projects and providing favorable research and data services for PoS projects.

name: Sanka Network
statement_en: Sanka Network is a leading validator in Asia market, who has been maintaining robust and secure infrastructure for staking blockchain with strong enthusiasm to achieve healthy governance and economy in the ecosystem. Delegate with us for your future earnings.
description_en: Sanka Network is backed by Tokyo-based blockchain company HashHub, Inc, which both are planning to contribute to the growth of IOST developer community by fostering relationships with community members in Asia market.

name: My IOST
statement: My IOST是全球第一个IOST生态钱包。致力于让使用场景融合和切换地更加自然，让用户体验简单、安全和强大的IOST资产管理工具。
description: My IOST是IOST生态入口及数字资产管理工具，应用汇集了最全最新的IOST资讯、节点投票、DApp动态等，拥有强大的管理功能与极高的安全系数。My IOST团队将不断优化IOST生态入口产品的架构，让使用场景融合和切换地更加自然，让用户体验简单、安全和强大的IOST资产管理工具。

name: NEST
statement: NEST 团队将联合 IOST 官方在去中心化金融领域展开深度合作，为 IOST 生态用户提供更多好用的 DeFi 产品和服务！
description: NEST 是一个去中心化金融（DeFi）服务生态协议。NEST DAPP 是基于 NEST 协议开发的去中心化应用，NEST DAPP 上的去中心化数字资产抵押借贷服务支持 ETH、USDT、HT、OMG、BAT、MKR、DAI、LOOM 等主流以太坊系资产之间的互相抵押借贷。其采用“链上合约”+“超额抵押”+“无需补仓”的机制，实现了真正意义上的数字资产去中心化、点对点的抵押借贷服务。

name: 没脸工作室
statement: 没脸没皮，天下无敌
description: 多年互联网、影视娱乐宣传推广运营经验，熟悉新媒体视频制作，参与上百个品牌、综艺节目、影视剧等项目的宣传物料策划制作。项目经历：爱奇艺《热血街舞团》、优酷《火星情报局》、央视《起航2018》跨年晚会、央视《我要上春晚》、张艺谋《对话·寓言2047》、北京卫视《但愿人长久》、电影《万万没想到》、医疗直播节目《悦悦来了》、别克《奇葩去哪儿》、深圳卫视《极速前进》、浙江卫视《蜜蜂少女队》、央视《“福寿中国”重阳晚会》、大麦网《麦叨》，央视《挑战不可能》、湖北卫视《非正式会谈》等；曾服务品牌：别克、I Do、自然堂、凯迪拉克等。

name: 慢雾区

name: Citadel
statement_en: At Paradigm Fund we strongly believe in a PoS economy of the future. According to our Network Valuation Model at least 71% of tokens in PoS ecosystem must be staked providing both a strong security and economic model. We envision Paradigm Citadel as a service gradually transforming into a network. Built around strongest projects in the field Citadel will provide state of the art user experience in consensus management (staking, delegation, guardianship) for HNWI, institutions and broad community. We consider IOST to be a unique and valuable type of asset. Combined with other fundamentally strong PoS networks scarce validator slots will enable second layer of sophisticated financial services and products to be built on top of them. This will allow IOST holders to get access to insurance pools, graph default swaps, crypto collateralized loans, tokenized PoS NFT`s and other financial products to be traded on our platform. Besides, we believe that bootstrapping community and ecosystem is as important as providing security and economic incentive. Our software team is experienced in developing a variety of tools for cryptonetworks. As an active community member we can develop specific tools needed for early stage of network development. On a community side, currently we have publishing bi-weekly IOST reports on our Medium and Twitter for almost a year, along with 30 min read in-depth report we published in July 2019.
description_en: Paradigm Fund is a group of industry experts and crypto enthusiasts, PhDs and graduates from the top universities investing in crypto space since 2013 with a strong track record including investments in top projects at ICO stages. We created Paradigm Citadel to provide a vast variety of support to the most promissing crypto projects including media coverage, developing tools for bootstrapping early stage ecosystems, launching nodes, participating in PoS systems as bakers/guardians/validators and other consensus model roles, providing community support.

description: DFG Crypto 是隶属 Digital Finance Group 旗下加密货币投资基金 （Token Fund）。Digital Finance Group 成立于 2015 年，是一个以投资、并购孵化为主的综合性集团公司，目前在全球拥有近 300 名员工，在上海、旧金山、阿布扎比、新加坡和首尔设有办事处。DFG 收购并孵化了多个区块链项目，包括：Matrix交易所，持有阿联酋国际金融中心（ADGM）颁发的 IPA 许可证的合规现货交易所；AToken，去中心化钱包，拥有 100 万用户和 50,000 日活；币卡丘，专业的市场行情精灵，拥有 50多 万注册用户，为投资者提供一站式的数字资产行情资讯服务，DFG 专为该项目收购了前 MyToken 的团队；以及在欧洲运营的 Exchange Union（交易所联盟）项目。
description_en: DFG Crypto is a Token Fund under Digital Finance Group.Founded in 2015, Digital Finance Group is a comprehensive group company with investment, M&A, and incubation as its main business. DFG now has nearly 300 employees around the globe, with offices in Shanghai, San Francisco, Abu Dhabi, Singapore and Seoul. Besides, we acquired and incubated several blockchain projects, including Matrix, a regulated spot exchange holding IPA license issued by Abu Dhabi (ADGM); AToken, a decentralized wallet with 1 million users and ~50,000 DAU; and BIKA, a professional market information product that provides investors with one-stop digital asset information services. We acquired the former Mytoken team to dedicate to it. And the Exchange Union project operated in Europe.

name: 库神钱包
description: 库神钱包成立于2016年11月，是中国首家冷钱包公司，曾两次入选工信部产业发展报告，也是国家高新技术企业。在17年完成了千万美金的融资，投资人包括火币、比特大陆和节点资本等。公司的使命是“区块链资产保护神”，愿景是成为“全球一流的区块链资产安全服务提供商”。库神目前拥有完善的的产品矩阵，包括ColdLar Pro系列（专业版硬件钱包），ColdLar Touch系列（卡式硬件钱包），APP钱包，云端钱包，库神加密资产多签管理系统ColdLar Vault系列，企业级钱包系统ColdLar Enterprise系列等。

name: IOST中文
description: IOST中文  是一个区块链技术和应用的信息窗口，我们会给大家带来全面的，及时的IOST最新的动态，欢迎大家关注和支持我们，谢谢！
description_en: IOST Chinese is an information window for blockchain technology and applications. We will bring you comprehensive, timely and latest IOST news. Welcome everyone to pay attention and support us, thank you!

name: bigIP影视动漫
statement: bigIP开发团队以实现IOST区块链技术服务实体经济为目标，着力打造影音娱乐行业“IOST信任链”；保护网络原创作者著作权，以孵化“大IP”为主要工作内容；为投资人选拔优秀IP；为用户建设新概念数字娱乐社区。
statement_en: The development team of bigIP aim at using IOST block chain technology to serve the real economy.We struggle to create audio-visual entertainment industry and protect the copyright of the web-based original creators.Our major tasks are to incubate the bigIP ,select the excellent IP for investors and build a new concept digital entertainment community for users.
description: bigIP电影动漫——是一个网络原创内容孵化系统和用户娱乐社区，原创作者可以发布剧本、小说、段子、漫画、音频、短视频、小游戏等作品，并拥有选票权和分红收益，平台会把“大IP”孵化为院线电影或网剧。用户在欣赏作品的同时具备投票权和分红权。投资人和广告商能够得到高质量项目和精准投放资源。而这一切都采用“去中心化思维”来建设，用户和作者最高享有80%的平台收入。
description_en: BigIP Movies and Animation is not only a web-based original content incubating system,but also an entertainment community for users. Original creators can issue the scripts novels,jokes,cartoons,audio,short videos,quick games and other works and they also enjoy voting rights and get divided income meanwhile.The platform will transform the bigIP into cinema film or Network drama. Users also have the voting rights and divided rights when they are appreciating the works.Both the investors and advertisers are able to get the high-quality projects and devote resources precisely.All of this is going to be built under the guidence of Decentering thought,so that the users and creators can get 80% revenue of platform maximumly.

name: Minglechain
statement_en: The strength of IOST is the strong united community, Minglechain helps to improve the interaction on all levels of the community. It doesn’t matter if you run a node, organise events, develop or just an enthusiast. It's not an IOST only location-based social network, it reaches new users to gain interested in IOST.The votes of IOST makes it possible to give support to event organisers. To attract more visitors, the app can be used as a communication platform and give raffles at events.Minglechain will add a wallet which makes it easy to buy premium, event tickets and advertisements or vote on IOST. Votes on Minglechain will go to the community and further development of Minglechain.
description_en: Minglechain is the world’s first location-based networking app for DLT/Blockchain professionals, companies and enthusiasts. Our tailor-made search feature and intuitive messaging function can help you find the contacts you need with minimal effort. Users will also be kept up to date with networking opportunities such as events, making Minglechain a one-stop-shop for Blockchain professionals. Use Minglechain’s free Android or iOS app to instantly connect with fellow blockchainers.https://www.minglechain.com/get
